\id ROM - Dawro 
\h Roome 
\toc3 Rom 
\toc2 Roome 
\toc1 Roome 
\mt2 Phawuloosi 
\mt1 Roome Asaw 
\mt2 Xaafeedda Kiitaa 
\imt1 Geluwaa 
\ip Yesuusi kiitteedda Phawuloosi Roome asaw xaafeedda kiitay, Phawuloosi Roomen de7iyaa woosa golliyaa xomoosanaw qoppeedda diraw, I baanaassi unttunttu giigiide naaganaadan oothanaassa. Phawuloosa qofay Roomen de7iyaa ammaniyaawanttunna guutha wodiyaa ootheeddawaappe guyyiyan, unttunttu maaddina Isippeene baanaassa. Kiristtinnaa ammanuwaabaa bare ereeddawaanne hewaa qassi ammaniyaa asay oosuwan peeshshana hanotaa qonccissiide xaafeedda. Phawuloosa qofay kumentha hanotaan beettiyaawe ha kiitaana. 
\ip Phawuloosi Roomen de7iyaa ammaniyaawanttussi sarotaa aathowaappenne unttunttoo woossanawaakka hidootaa immowaappe guyyiyaan, kiitaassi giddo qofay “Mishiraachchuwaa qaalay Xoossay asaa xillissiyaawe, koyruwaappe wurssethaa gakkanaw ammanuwaana gidiyaawaa odee” (1:17) 
\ip Hewaappe guyyiyan Phawuloosi ha qofaa aassiide xaafee. Ayihudatuwaa gidinakka Ayihuda gidenna asaa gidinakka ubbay nagaraw moodettiyaawantta gidiyaa diraw, unttunttu Xoossaanna sigettanaw koshshee. Asay Xoossaanna sigettanaw danddayiyaawe Yesuusi Kiristtoosan ammaniyaawaana. Xoossaanna medhdhiyaa ooratha ittippetethaa ayfi ooratha de7uwaa gidiyaawaa Phawuloosi aassiide odeedda. Ammaniyaa asay Xoossaanna saro de7ee. Qassi Xoossaa Ayyaanaa bagganna nagaraanne hayquwaa wolqqaappe bilettee. Phawuloosi Xoossaa qofaynne ammaniyaa asaa de7uwaa giddon oothiyaa Xoossaa Ayyaanaa wolqqaa qofay ayentto odee (5-8). Hewaappe kaalliide qassi Phawuloosi, “Xoossay asaa naanaassi qoppeedda qofaa giddon Ayihudatuunne Ayihuda gidenna asatuu waaniide ittippe waaxettanaw danddayanawantteeshsha?” yaagiyaa ooshaa zaaranaw baaxetiidde de7ee. 
\ip Qassikka Phawuloosi, Ayihudatuu Yesuusa akkennaan aggeeddawe Xoossaa qofaa gidiyaawaa odee. Ayissi gooppe, hawaa mala hanotaan asaa zerethay ubbay Xoossay Yesuusa bagganna qonccisseedda aadho keekatethaan ittippetethaa oothanaassa. Gidoshshin, Ayihudatuu Yesuusa akkanaw wodii yaanawaa Phawuloosi ammanee. Wurssethaan Phawuloosi Kiristtinnaa de7uwaa waaniide de7anaw bessintto odee. Xoossaassi oothanabaa, ammaniyaa asatuu barenttu gadiyaassinne barenttu giddon ittu ittuwaassi siiquwaaninne maataan oothanabaanne qofaa gaasuwan denddiyaa ooshatuwaabaa qonccissiide odee. 
\iot Shemppatuwaa Ubbatuwassi Imetteedda Qantha Qofatuwaa 
\io1 Roome kiitaa huuphe qofaa geluwaa (1:1-17) 
\io1 Atotethay asaw koshshiyaawaa gidiyaawaa (1:18-3:20) 
\io1 Xoossaa ashshuwaa ogiyaa (3:21-4:25) 
\io1 Yesuusan beettiyaa oratha de7uwaa (5:1-8:39) 
\io1 Isra7eeliyaa asaw de7iyaa Xoossaa qofaa (9:1-11:36) 
\io1 Kiristtinnaassi bessiyaa oosuwaa (12:1-15:13) 
\io1 Wursethaa qofaanne sarotaa (15:14-16:27) 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Bare mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa odanaw Xoossay dooriide xeeseedda Kiristtoosa Yesuusa qoomay, Yesuusi Kiristtoosi kiitteedda Phawuloosi, taani ha dabidaabbiyaa xaafay. 
\p  
\v 2 Xoossay daro wodeppe kase bare nabatuwaa bagganna mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa immana yaageeddawe Xoossaa Geeshsha Maxaafatuwan xaafetteedda;  
\v 3 he mishiraachchuwaa qaalay asa gidiide Daawite zariyaappe yeletteedda Xoossaa Na7aa, nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosabaa.  
\v 4 Qassi I bare Geeshsha Ayyaanaan \f + \fr 1:4 \fq bare Geeshsha Ayyaanan: \ft woy “Aani de7iyaa Geeshsha Ayyaanaa”\f* hayquwaappe denddeeddawaan, Xoossaa Na7aa gidiyaawaa wolqqaama wolqqaan besseedda.  
\v 5 Ayihuda gidenna asay ubbay ammananaadaaninne azazettanaadan, nuuni unttuntta kaalethana mala, Xoossay Kiristtoosa sunthaa diraw, Kiristtoosa bagganna aadho keekatethaanne Yesuusi kiitteeddawantta gidiyaa maataa nuussi immeedda.  
\v 6 Yesuusi Kiristtoosawaa gidanaadan, Xoossay xeeseedda hinttenttukka hewanttu giddon de7iita. 
\p  
\v 7 Xoossay siiqiyaawanttoonne geeshshabaa oothanaw xeeseedda Roome gadiyan de7iyaa ubbatoo Xoossaa nu Aawuwaappenne Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosappe aadho keekatethaynne sarotethay hinttenttoo gido. 
\s1 Galataa Woosaa 
\p  
\v 8 Kasetaade taani hinttenttu ammanuu sa7aa ubbaan sisetteedda diraw, Yesuusi Kiristtoosa bagganna hinttenttoo taani Xoossaa galatay.  
\v 9-10 Ayissi gooppe, taani ubba wode ta woosaan hinttentta hassayissiyaawoo, Xoossay, taani A Na7aa mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa odiyaawaan ta ayyaanan aw oothiyaawe markka. Xoossay, bare sheniyaan, taani ha77i hinttenttukko baanaw ta ogiyaa miikkoyanaadaan, ubba wode woossay.  
\v 11 Ayissi gooppe, taani hinttentta minissanaw, hinttenttunna ittippe Ayyaanaa imotaa shaakkana mala, hinttentta be7anaw laamotay.  
\v 12 Taani giyaawe, hinttenttukka takka itti wode minettana. Hinttenttu ta ammanuwan, qassi taanikka hintte ammanuwan minettana. 
\p  
\v 13 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, taani ubba wode hinttenttukko baanaw qoppaaddi. Shin taana diggiyaabay de7iyaawaa hintte eranaw bessee; taani haray atto Ayihuda gidenna hara asaappekka ayfiyaa demmeeddawaadan, hinttenttuppekka ayfiyaa demmanaw koyyay.  
\v 14 Taani asaa ubbaw, Giriike asawunne tamaaribeenna asaw qassi aadho eranchchatoonne eeyatoo qanxxana acuu de7ee. 
\p  
\v 15 Hewaa diraw, taw danddayetteedda keenaan Roomen de7iyaa hinttenttussikka mishiraachchuwaa qaalaa odanaw amottay. 
\s1 Mishiraachchuwaa Qaalay Xoossaa Wolqqaa 
\p  
\v 16 Mishiraachchuwaa qaalay taana yeellayenna; I ammaniyaa ubbaa, kasetiide Ayihuda asaa qassi Ayihuda gidenna asaa ashshanaw Xoossaappe yiyaa wolqqaa.  
\v 17 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa Maxaafay, “Xilluu Xoossaan ammanettiide de7ana” yaagiyaawaadan, Xoossay asaa koyroppe wurssethaa gakkanaw, ammanuwan xillissiyaawaa mishiraachchuwaa qaalay qonccissee. \x - \xo 1:17 \xt Ibr 2:4\x* 
\s1 Asaa Iita Oosuwaa 
\p  
\v 18 Tumatethay erettanawaa barenttu iita hanotaan diggiyaa nagaraa oosuwaa ubbaa bollaninne asaa iita oosuwaa ubbaa bollan, Xoossaa hanqquu saluwaappe wodhdhiide qonccana.  
\v 19 Unttunttu Xoossaabaa erana danddayiyaawe unttunttoo qonccee; ayissi gooppe, Xoossay unttunttoo qonccisseedda.  
\v 20 Beettenna A hanotay, hewekka A medhinaa wolqqaynne A Xoossatethay ittippe Xoossay ha alamiyaa medhdheeddawaappe doommiide, unttunttoo qoncciide beetteedda; unttunttu hewaa Xoossay medhdheeddabaappe be7anaw danddayiyaa diraw, unttunttoo gaasoyiyaabay baawa. 
\p  
\v 21 Ayissi gooppe, unttunttu Xoossaa erooppekka, aw bessiyaa bonchchuwaa immibeykkino; qassi A galatikkino. Shin unttunttu allaalle kessennabaa qooppiino; qassi unttunttu akeekenna wozanay dhumeedda.  
\v 22 Unttunttu barentta aadhdheedda eranchcha giino; shin unttunttu eeya.  
\v 23 Unttunttu hayqqenna Xoossaassi goyinniyaawaa ixxiide, hayqqiyaa asaa medhetaa, kafatuwaa medhetaa, do7atuwaa medhetaanne tiraan gooshettiyaawanttu medhetaa medhetteeddawanttussi goyinneeddino. \x - \xo 1:23 \xt Zar 4:16-18\x* 
\p  
\v 24 Hewaa diraw, unttunttu ittu ittuwaanna pokkobaa oothana mala, Xoossay unttunttu wozanay amottiyaa tunabaa oothanaadan unttuntta aggeedda.  
\v 25 Ayissi gooppe, unttunttu Xoossaa tumatethaa wordduwan laammeeddino; qassi medhdheedda Xoossaa aggiide, I medheeddabaw goyinneeddinonne ootheeddino. Xoossay medhinaw galatetteeddawaa. Amen77i. 
\p  
\v 26 Hewaa diraw, Xoossay unttunttu pokkobaa amottana mala, unttuntta aggeedda; haray atto unttunttu maccawanttu barenttoo bessiyaawaa aggiide, bessennawaa haneeddino.  
\v 27 Hawaadankka, attuma asay qassi barenttoo bessiyaawaadan maccawanttunna gakettiyaawaa aggiide, ittu ittuwaanna gakettanaw koyyeeddino; attuma asay ittu ittuwaanna pokkobaa oothiide, barenttu ootheedda balaan barenttoo bessiyaa pirddaa akkeeddino. 
\p  
\v 28 Unttunttu Xoossaa eranaw dosennaan ixxeeddawaa keenaa Xoossay unttunttu bessennawaa oothana mala, unttunttoo pathenna qofaa immeedda.  
\v 29 Unttunttun tunatethay, iitatethay, yoratethaynne iita hanotay kumeedda; qassi unttunttun qanaatii, shemppuwaa wodhiyaa qofay, palumay, cimmussaynne iita qofay kumeedda; qassi unttunttu soqiyaawantta,  
\v 30 zigiriyaawantta, Xoossaa ixxiyaawantta, boriyaawantta, otorettiyaawantta, ceeqettiyaawantta, iitabaa oothanaw koyyiyaawanttanne barenttu aawoonne aattiw azazettennawantta,  
\v 31 qofay baynnawantta, ammanuu baynnawantta, haranttoo qarettennawanttanne maarennawantta.  
\v 32 Unttunttu hawanttu malaa oothiyaawanttussi hayquu bessee giyaa Xoossaa higgiyaa eriidde, hawantta oothiino; hewaa xalalaa gidennaan, hawantta oothiyaawanttakka oothite giide minissiino. 
\c 2  
\s1 Xoossaa Pirddaa 
\p  
\v 1 Hewaa diraw, neenoo haranttu bolla pirddiyaawoo, new gaasoyiyaabay baawa; ayissi gooppe, neeni haranttu bolla pirddaadde, he neeni unttunttu bolla pirddiyaawaa malaa udooppe, ne bolla pirddaasa.  
\v 2 Nuuni hawaa mala oosuwaa oothiyaawanttu bolla Xoossay xillo pirddaa pirddiyaawaa ereetto.  
\v 3 Neenoo, hawaa mala oosuwaa oothiyaawanttu bolla pirddiyaawoo, qassi he neeni pirddiyaawaa malaa oothiyaawoo, neeni Xoossaa pirddaappe attiyaawaa malatii?  
\v 4 Woy Xoossaa wolqqaama keekatethaa, genccuwaanne danddayaa kadhayishsha? Xoossay neena nagaraappe zaaranaw koyyiyaa diraw, I keeka gidiyaawaa neeni eraasa. 
\p  
\v 5 Shin hinttenttoo guzuma wozanaynne nagaraappe simmenna wozanay de7ee; hewaa diraw, Xoossaa hanqquunne xillo pirdday qoncciyaa gallassi, neeni ne bolla hanqquwaa kasewaappe darissaasa.  
\v 6 Xoossay asaa ubbaw A oosuwaa malaa immanawaa. \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Maz 62:12; Lem 24:12\x* 
\v 7 Itti itti asatuu lo77obaa danddayan oothiino; qassi galataa, bonchchuwaanne bayenna de7uwaa koyyiino; unttunttoo Xoossay medhinaa de7uwaa immana.  
\v 8 Shin haranttu iitabaa oothanaw yaaretiinonne tumatethaa ixxiino; Xoossay unttunttu bolla bashshaanne hanqquwaa yeddana.  
\v 9 Iitabaa oothiyaa asay ubbay metootananne waayyettana; hewe kasetiide, Ayihuda asaa gakkana; hewaappe qassi Ayihuda gidenna asaa gakkana.  
\v 10 Shin Xoossay lo77o oosuwaa oothiyaa ubbatoo galataa, bonchchuwaanne sarotethaa immana. Kasetiide Ayihudatoo immana; hewaappe qassi Ayihuda gidennawanttoo immana.  
\v 11 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa Ayifiyan asay ubbay itti mala. \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Zar 10:17\x* 
\p  
\v 12 Muse higgii baynnaan nagaraa ootheedda ubbay higgii baynnaan dhayana. Muse higgii de7ishshin, nagaraa ootheedda ubbay higgiyan pirddettana.  
\v 13 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa sinthan higgiyaa naagiyaawanttu xilliinoppe attin, higgiyaa sisiyaawanttu xillikkino.  
\v 14 Ayihuda gidenna asaw higgii baawa; shin barenttu tilla qofaan higgii azaziyaawaa oothiino; unttunttoo higgii dhayooppekka, unttunttu barenttu huuphew higge.  
\v 15 Higgii azaziyaawe unttunttu wozanaa giddon xaafetteeddawaa unttunttu hanotay bessee; itti itti kaalla unttunttu tilla qofay unttunttoo markkattiyaa dirawunne qassi itti itti kaalla unttunttu qofay unttuntta mootiyaa diraw, woy qassi unttunttunna gaaddatiyaa diraw, hewe tuma gidiyaawaa erissee.  
\v 16 Taani tamaarisseedda mishiraachchuwaa qaalaadan, asaa wozanaan geemmeedda qofaa Xoossay Yesuusi Kiristtoosa bagganna hawaadan pirddana. 
\s1 Ayihudatuwaanne Muse Higgiyaa 
\p  
\v 17 Shin neeni neena Ayihuda gaasa; higgiyan zemppaade Xoossaan ceeqettaasa.  
\v 18 Neeni oothana mala, Xoossay koyyiyaawe ayentto eraa; qassi tuma gidiyaawaa dooranaw higgiyaappe tamaaraadda.  
\v 19-20 Neeni qooqatuwaa kaalethiyaawaa, qassi dhumaani de7iyaawanttookka poo7issiyaawaa, erennawantta erissiyaawaanne naanatuwaa tamaarissiyaawaa gidiyaawaa eraaddi; higgiyaappe neeni kumentha eratethaanne tumatethaa demmiyaawaa eraasa.  
\v 21 Yaatina, neeni haratuwaa tamaarissiyaawe neena ne huuphew ayissi tamaarissikkii? Neeni, “Wuu77oppa” yaagaade qaalaa odaasa. Shin neeni ne huuphew wuu77ayee?  
\v 22 Neeni, “Woshummoppa” yaagaa. Shin neeni ne huuphew woshummay? Neeni eeqaa shenetaa. Shin eeqay de7iyaa golliyaa bonqqay?  
\v 23 Xoossaa higgii new de7iyaa diraw, neeni ceeqettaasa; shin he higgiyaa menthaade Xoossaa yeellayay?  
\v 24 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa Maxaafay, “Ayihuda asatoo, hintte gaasuwan Ayihuda gidenna asatuwaa giddon Xoossaa sunthay bayee” yaagee. \x - \xo 2:24 \xt Isa 52:5\x* 
\p  
\v 25 Neeni higgew azazettooppe, ne qaxxaray maaduwanna de7ee; shin neeni higgiyaa menthooppe, neeni qaxxaretteeddawe qaxxarettibeennawaadan paydettee.  
\v 26 Ayihuda gidenna asay qaxxarettennan higgii azaziyaawaa naagooppe, Xoossay A qaxxaretteeddawaadan paydennee?  
\v 27 Hinttenttu, Ayihuda asatuu, hinttenttoo xaafetteedda higgii de7ooppekka qassi hintte qaxxarettooppekka, higgiyaa hintte menthiyaa diraw, Ayihuda gidenna asay bollaa qaxxarettana dhayooppekka, higgew azazettiide, hintte bolla pirddana. 
\p  
\v 28 Ayissi gooppe, Ayihuda asaa malatiyaa ubbay tumu Ayihuda asa gidenna; qassi asay bare ashuwaa asatethaa qaxxaretteedda diraw, tumu Ayihuda asa gidenna.  
\v 29 Shin tumu Ayihuda asa giyaa uray garssa bagganna Ayihuda asa \f + \fr 2:29 \ft Ayihuda guussay galatettiyaawaa gidiide sunthay Yihudaappe yeedda.\f* gideeddawaa; qaxxarettiyaawaa Xoossaa Ayyaanan oosettiyaa wozanaa qaxxaraappe attin, xaafetteedda higgiyaana gidenna; he uray bare galataa Xoossaappe akkiyawaappe attin, asaappe akkibeenna. \x - \xo 2:29 \xt Zar 30:6\x* 
\c 3  
\s1 Ayihudatuu Ammanennaan Aggussaan Bayizzeeddino 
\p  
\v 1 Yaatina, Ayihuda asatuu ayaani Ayihuda gidenna asaappe aadhdhiinoo? Woy qaxxarettiyaawaan ay maaduu de7ii?  
\v 2 Hawe Ayihudatuwaa ubbabaani loythi maaddee; ubbabaappe kase Xoossay bare kiitaa hadaraa Ayihudatoo immeedda. 
\p  
\v 3 Yaatina unttunttuppe ittu ittuu ammanettennawaa gidooppe, waanii? Hewaa diraw, Xoossay ammanettenna yaagiyaawee?  
\v 4 Hewaa gidenna; asay ubbay worddanchchaa gidooppekka, Xoossay giyaawe tuma gidanaw bessee. Xoossaa Maxaafay, “Neeni haasayiyaa wode, neeni xillo gidiyaawaa erissanaw koshshee; neeni mootettiyaa wode, shatimmanaw bessee” yaagee. \x - \xo 3:4 \xt Maz 51:4\x* 
\p  
\v 5 Shin nu bayizzuu Xoossaa xillo oosuwaa erissintto, nuuni waaganee? Nu bolla hanqquwaa ahiyaa Xoossay bayizzanchchee? Taani asay giyaawaadan gay.  
\v 6 Hewe waayyii hanana. Ayissi gooppe, hewaadan gidooppe, Xoossay ha alamiyaa bolla wooti pirddanee? 
\p  
\v 7 Shin ta wordduwan Xoossaa tumatethay A bonchchoo darooppe, yaatina, hawaa gakkanaw ayissi ta bolla nagaranchchaadan pirddii?  
\v 8 Yaatina nuuni, “Lo77uu yaanaadan, ane iitabaa oothoytte” ayissi gookkoo? Itti itti asay hawaa taana mootiidde boreeddino; unttunttu Xoossaappe bessiyaa pirddaa akkana. 
\s1 Asay Ubbay Nagaranchchaa 
\p  
\v 9 Hewaa diraw, nuuni waaganee? Nuuni Ayihudatuu, Ayihuda gidenna asaappe dareettoo? Hewaa gidenna; ayissi gooppe, Ayihudatuukka Ayihuda gidenna asatuukka ubbay ittippe nagaraappe garssan de7iyaawaa taani kase hinttenttoo odaaddi. 
\p  
\v 10 Xoossaa Maxaafay hawaadan yaagee; \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Maz 14:1-3\x* 
\q1 “Xillo asay ittuunne baawa. 
\q1  
\v 11 Akeekiyaa asaykka baawa; 
\q2 woy Xoossaa koyyiyaawekka baawa. 
\q1  
\v 12 Asay ubbay ogiyaappe kare keseeddino; 
\q2 ubbay mulekka maaddennawaa gideedda. 
\q2 Lo77obaa oothiyaa ooninne baawa; 
\q2 haray atto ittuunne baawa. 
\q1  
\v 13 Unttunttu doonay dooya de7iyaa duufuwaa mala. 
\q2 Barenttu inxxarssan worddoteeddino. 
\q2 Unttunttu doonaappe asaa wodhiyaa shooshshaa 
\q2 yishsha mala haasayay kesee. \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Maz 5:9\x* 
\q1  
\v 14 Unttunttu doonaan sheqaynne camobay kumeedda. \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Maz 10:7\x* 
\q1  
\v 15 Unttunttu suuthaa gussanaw 
\q2 darii elleelliino. \x - \xo 3:15 \xt Isa 59:7-8\x* 
\q1  
\v 16 Bayzzuunne kolethay 
\q2 unttunttu beeddasaan haqaninne dhayenna. 
\q1  
\v 17 Unttunttu sarotethaa ogiyaakka erikkino. 
\q1  
\v 18 Qassi Xoossaw yayyiyaabay 
\q2 unttunttu qofaan baawa” 
\m yaagee. \x - \xo 3:18 \xt Maz 36:1\x* 
\p  
\v 19 Asaa ubbaa haasayaa diggana malanne kumentha sa7aa Xoossaa pirddaappe garssaw aathana mala, higgiyaa giddon odetteedda ubbabay higgiyaappe garssan de7iyaa asaw haasayiyaawaa nuuni ereetto.  
\v 20 Xoossaa sinthan ooninne higgii azaziyaawaa oothiyaawaan xillenna; higgii itti asay nagaraa ootheeddawaa eranaadan udee. \x - \xo 3:20 \xt Maz 143:2; Gal 2:16\x* 
\s1 Asay Xilliyaawe Ammanuwaana 
\p  
\v 21 Shin Xoossay asaa xillissiyaa ogii higgii baynnaan ha77i qoncceedda; higgiinne nabatuu he xillotethaabaa markkatteeddino.  
\v 22 Xoossay asaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa ammaniyaawaan xillissee; Xoossay hewaa A ammaniyaa ubbaw oothee; ay shaakotethaynne baawa. 
\p  
\v 23 Ayissi gooppe, asay ubbay nagaraa ootheedda; Xoossaa bonchchuukka unttunttoo guuxxeedda.  
\v 24 Shin unttunttu Xoossay immiyaa A aadho keekatethaan, barentta woziyaa Kiristtoosi Yesuusa bagganna coo xilleeddino.  
\v 25 Yesuusa suuthaan asay A ammaniide, bare nagaraw maarotethaa demmanaw, Xoossay A immeedda; Xoossay hewaa bare xillotethaa bessanaw ootheedda; I beni wodiyaan asaa nagaraa danddayiide, kadhi bashi aggeedda; shin  
\v 26 ha wodiyaan bare xillotethaa bessanaw asaa nagaraa aggenna; Xoossay hewaa oothiyaawaan I bare huuphew xillo gidiyaawaanne Yesuusa ammaniyaa ubbaa xillissiyaawaa bessee. 
\p  
\v 27 Yaatina, nuuni ayaw ceeqettanee? Aynne baawa. Ayaa gasuwaanee? Nuuni higgew eeno giyaawaanee? Gidenna; ammanuwaa higgiyaanappe attin.  
\v 28 Ayissi gooppe, asay ammanuwan xillanaappe attin, higgii azaziyaawaa oothiyaawaana gidenna yaagiide qoppeetto. 
\p  
\v 29 Woy Xoossay Ayihudatuwaa xalalaw Xoossee? Ayihuda gidenna asaw Xoossaa gidennee? Tuma, Ayihuda gidennawanttookka I qassi Xoossaa.  
\v 30 Itti Xoossaa xalalay de7ee; Ayihudatuwaa unttunttu ammanuwan I xillissana; qassi Ayihuda gidennawanttakka unttunttu ammanuwan xillissana. \x - \xo 3:30 \xt Zar 6:4; Gal 3:20\x* 
\v 31 Yaatina, nuuni higgiyaa ammanuwan gaxaa suganee? Gidenna; higgiyaa minissoytteppe attin. 
\c 4  
\s1 Abraahaamo Ammanuwan Xilleedda 
\p  
\v 1 Yaatina, nuuni nuussi ashuwan zare gidiyaa Abraahaamo ayaa demmeedda gaanee?  
\v 2 Ayissi gooppe, Abraahaamo oosuwan xilleeddawaa gidooppe, aw ceeqettiyaabay de7ee; shin Xoossaa sinthan ceeqettana danddayenna.  
\v 3 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa Maxaafay waagii? “Abraahaamo Xoossaa ammaneedda; Xoossay hewaa aw xillotethaan paydeedda” yaagee. \x - \xo 4:3 \xt Dom 15:6; Gal 3:6\x* 
\p  
\v 4 Oothiyaa uray akkiya miishshaa barew bessina akkeeppe attin, aw coo imettiyaawaadan paydettenna.  
\v 5 Shin oosuwaa oothennaan, nagaranchchaa xillissiyaa Xoossaa ammaniyaa uraa, Xoossay A ammanuwan A xillissee.  
\v 6 Hawaadankka, ay oosuunne baynnaan, Xoossay xilluwaadan paydeedda asaa nashechchiyaabaa Daawite haasayeedda wode geeddawe hawaa. 
\q1  
\v 7 “Xoossay unttunttu bayizzuwaa 
\q2 atto geeddawanttunne 
\q1 unttunttu nagaraa kammeeddawanttu 
\q2 anjjetteeddawantta. \x - \xo 4:7 \xt Maz 32:1-2\x* 
\q1  
\v 8 Goday A nagaraa paydenna asay 
\q2 anjjetteeddawaa” 
\m yaagee. 
\p  
\v 9 Yaatina, ha Daawite hasayeedda anjjuu qaxxaretteedda asaa xalalaasseeyee? Woy qassi qaxxarettibeenna asatuwaassee? Ayissi gooppe nuuni, “Xoossaa Maxaafay, ‘Abraahaamo Xoossaa ammaneedda; Xoossay hewaa aw xillotethaan paydeedda’ yaagee” goytte.  
\v 10 Yaatina, hawe awude haneeddee? Abraahaamo qaxxaretti simmineyee? Woy qaxxarettanaappe kasennee? Qaxxarettanaappe kasennappe attin, qaxxarettina gidenna. 
\p  
\v 11 Guyyeppe I qaxxaretteedda; Xoossay A ammanuwaa diraw, I qaxxarettanaappe kase A xillo udeeddawaa erissanaw, A qaxxaray malla gideedda. Hewekka qassi qaxxarettennan Xoossaa ammaniyaa ubbatuwaa Xoossay xillo oothiide paydanaadan, unttunttoo Abraahaamo aawuwaa gidanaassa. \x - \xo 4:11 \xt Dom 17:10\x* 
\v 12 I qaxxaretteeddawanttookka aawuwaa; gidooppekka, unttunttu qaxxaretteedda diraassa gidenna; shin nu aawuwaa Abraahaamo qaxxarettanaappe kase ammaniyaa ammanuwaa malaa kaalliyaawanttookka aawuwaa. 
\s1 Xoossay Immana Geeddabay Ammanuwan Akettee 
\p  
\v 13 Abraahaamossinne A zerethaw Xoossay, “Ha sa7aa taani hinttenttoo immana” yaageeddawe, Abraahaamo Xoossaa ammaniide xilleedda diraassappe attin, higgew I azazetteedda diraassa gidenna. \x - \xo 4:13 \xt Dom 17:4-6; 22:17-18; Gal 3:29\x* 
\v 14 Ayissi gooppe, higgew azazettiyaawanttu Xoossay immana geeddawaa laattiyaawantta gidooppe, asaa ammanuu maaddennabaa gideedda; Xoossay geeddawekka mela gideedda;  
\v 15 higgii Xoossaa boshaa ahee; shin higgii baynnasaan higgiyaa menthiyaabay baawa. 
\p  
\v 16-17 Hewaa diraw, higgiyaa naagiyaawanttu xalalaw gidennaan, qassi Abraahaamo ammaneeddawaadan, ammaniyaa Abraahaame zerethaa ubbaw Xoossay immana geeddawe, woytaadan tumattanawe ammanuwaana. Abraahaamo nuussi ubbaw aawuwaa. Xoossaa Maxaafay, “Taani neena cora kawutethatoo aawo oothaaddi” giyaawaadan, hayqqeeddawanttoo de7uwaa immiyaa, bare azazuwan baynnabaa de7iyaabaadan oothiide xeesiyaa, I ammaneedda Xoossaa sinthan Abraahaamo nuussi ubbaw aawuwaa. \x - \xo 4:16-17 \xt Dom 17:5\x* 
\p  
\v 18 Xoossaa Maxaafay Abraahaamossi, “Ne zerethay hawaa keena gidana” yaageeddawaadan, hawaa keena gidana giide, nashechchaan naaganaw danddayenna wode, Abraahaamo ammaniidenne sinthappe demmana giide, nashechchaan naagiide, cora zerethaw aawuwaa gideedda. \x - \xo 4:18 \xt Dom 15:5\x* 
\v 19 He wode, Abraahaamo yelettoodeppe xeetu laythaa kumana haniyaa cimaa; shin bare daaburanchcha asatethaanne Saara na7aa yelanaw danddayennawaa qoppeedda wode, I bare ammanuwan daaburibeenna. \x - \xo 4:19 \xt Dom 17:17\x* 
\p  
\v 20-21 Xoossaa I bonchchiidde, aw immana geedda Xoossay qassi polanaw danddayiyaawaa loythi eriide bare ammanuwan minneeddawaappe attin, ammanennaan ixxiide, Xoossay immana geeddawaa sidhibeenna.  
\v 22 Hewaa diraw, Xoossay qassi A ammanuwaa xillotethaan paydeedda. 
\p  
\v 23 “Aw xillotethaan paydeedda” giyaa qaalay A xalalaw xaafettibeenna.  
\v 24 He qaalay nu Godaa Yesuusa hayquwaappe dentheedda Xoossaa ammaniyaa nuussikka xillotethaan paydettana mala xaafetteedda.  
\v 25 Xoossay A nu nagaraa diraw, hayqoo aathiide immina, I nuuna xillissanaw hayquwaappe denddeedda. \x - \xo 4:25 \xt Isa 53:4-5\x* 
\c 5  
\s1 Ammanuwan Beettiyaa Sarotethaanne Sigatethaa 
\p  
\v 1 Hewaa diraw, nuuni ammanuwan xilleeddawaan, nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa bagganna nuussi Xoossaanna sarotethay de7ee;  
\v 2 qassi I nuuna ha77i nuuni de7iyaa Xoossaa aadho keekatethaa giddo ammanuwan aheedda; yaatina, nuuni Xoossaa bonchchuwaa shaakkanaw nuussi de7iyaa hidootaan ceeqetteetto. 
\p  
\v 3-4 Hewaa xalalaa gidenna; nuuni nu waayyiyankka nashetteetto; ayissi gooppe, waayyiyaappe danddayay, qassi danddayaappe paaciyaan minniyaawe, paaciyaan minotaappe hidootay yiyaawaa nuuni ereetto.  
\v 5 Xoossay nuussi immeedda Geeshsha Ayyaanaa bagganna bare siiquwaa nu wozanaan gusseedda diraw, he nuuni demmanaw nashechchaan naagi utteeddawe nuuna yeellayenna. 
\p  
\v 6 Ayissi gooppe, nuuni biro wolqqay baynnawantta gidiide de7ishshin, Xoossay dooreedda wodii gakkina, Kiristtoosi nagaranchchatuwaa diraw hayqqeedda.  
\v 7 Xillo uraa diraw, itti uray hayqqanawe daro metobaa; shin lo77o asaa diraw hayqqanaw, “Eeno” giyaa uray ooni eri beettennaan aggenna.  
\v 8 Shin nuuni biro nagaranchcha gidiide de7ishshin, Kiristtoosi nu diraw hayqqeedda; hewe Xoossay nuuna ay keenaa siiqinttonne A siiquwaa erissee.  
\v 9 Simmi nuuni ha77i A suuthaan xilleeddawaa gidooppe, A bagganna Xoossaa hanqquwaappe attana.  
\v 10 Ayissi gooppe, nuuni Xoossaanna kase morkke; shin A Na7aa hayquwan aananna sigetteeddo. Hewaappe aathiide, ha77i nuuni Xoossaanna sigetteeddaawaappe guyyiyan, I paxa gidiyaa diraw nuuna ashshana.  
\v 11 Shin hewaa xalalaa gidenna; ha77i nuuna Xoossaanna sigetheedda nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa bagganna nuuna Xoossaabay nashechchee. 
\s1 Hayquu Addaaman Yiina, De7uu Kiristtoosan Yeedda 
\p  
\v 12 Hewaa diraw, nagaray ha sa7aa itti asaa bagganna geleedda; he nagaray barenanna hayquwaa aheedda; hewaa gaasuwan, asay ubbay Addaama bagganna nagaraa ootheedda diraw, hayquu asaa zariyaa ubbaa gakkeedda. \x - \xo 5:12 \xt Dom 3:6\x* 
\v 13 Higgii imettanaappe kase, ha alamiyaan nagaray de7ee; shin higgii baynna wode nagaray paydettenna.  
\v 14 Shin Addaama wodiyaappe, Muse wodiyaa gakkanaassi, hayquu asaa ubbaa mooddeedda; haray atto Addaami Xoossaa higgew azazettennan ixxeeddawaadan, nagaraa oothibeennawanttakka hayquu mooddeedda. 
\p Ayissi gooppe, Addaami yaanawoo leemisuwaa.  
\v 15 Shin Xoossaa imotay Addaama nagaraa keena gidenna diraw, unttunttu itti mala gidikkino; itti bitaniyaa nagaraa diraw, cora asay hayqqeeddawe tuma; shin Xoossaa aadho keekatethaynne A imotay itti asaa aadho keekatethaa bagganna, Yesuusi Kiristtoosa aadho keekatethaa bagganna cora asaw dareedda.  
\v 16 Xoossaa imotay nagaraa ootheedda bitaniyaa bagganna yeeddawaa mala gidenna; ayissi gooppe, Addaami itti nagaraa ootheeddawaappe guyyiyan, Xoossay A bayizzeeddawaadan pirddeedda; shin asay daro nagaraa ootheeddawaappe guyyiyan Xoossay, “Hinttenttu bayizzibeykkita” giide, bare aadho keekatethaa unttuntta bessee.  
\v 17 Ayissi gooppe, itti bitaniyaa nagaraa gaasuwan, A nagaraa bagganna, hayquu kawuteeddawe tuma; shin itti uray, Yesuusi Kiristtoosi ootheeddabay ay keena daree; Xoossaa daro aadho keekatethaanne xillotethaa imotaa akkiya ubbay Kiristtoosa bagganna xooniide de7ana. 
\p  
\v 18 Simmi itti uray nagaraa ootheedda gaasuwan asaa ubbaa bolla bayizzeeddawaadan pirdday yeedda. Hewaadankka itti uray xillobaa ootheedda gaasuwan, Xoossay asaa ubbaa, “Bayzzibeykkita” giide unttunttoo de7uwaa immeedda.  
\v 19 Ayissi gooppe, itti uray azazettennan ixxeedda gaasuwan, daro asay nagaranchcha gideedda, hawaadankka qassi ittuu eeno geeddawaan cora asay xillana. 
\p  
\v 20 Nagaraa darissanaw, higgii yeedda; shin nagaray dariyaa wode Xoossaa aadho keekatethay loythi dareedda.  
\v 21 Nagaray hayquwaa wolqqaan kawuteeddawaadan, hawaadankka qassi Xoossaa aadho keekatethay xillotethaa wolqqaan kawutiide, nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa bagganna, nuuna medhinaa de7oo kaalethee. 
\c 6  
\s1 Nagaraappe Shaakettiide Kiristtoosan De7ussaa 
\p  
\v 1 Yaatina, nuuni waaganee? Xoossaa aadho keekatethay daranaadan, nagaraan minniide de7anee?  
\v 2 Gidenna; nuuni nagaraa oothenna mala hayqqidiggeeddo. Yaatina, nuuni hawaappe sinthaw wooti A giddon de7anee?  
\v 3 Woy nuuni ubbatuu Kiristtoosa Yesuusanna ittippe gidanaw, xammaqetteedda wode, A hayquwankka aananna ittippe gidanaw xammaqetteeddawaa erikkitee?  
\v 4 Hewaa diraw, Kiristtoosi bare Aawuwaa bonchcho wolqqaan hayquwaappe denddowaadan, nuunikka ooratha de7uwaa de7anaw, A hayquwaa aananna shaakkanaw xinqqataani aananna ittippe moogetteeddo. 
\p  
\v 5 Ayissi gooppe, nuuni I hayqqeeddawaadan hayqqiide, aananna ittuwaa gidooppe, hawaadankka, hayquwaappe I denddowaadan nuunikka denddiide, aananna ittuwaa gidana.  
\v 6 Nuuni hawaappe sinthaw nagaraw aylle gidenna mala, qassi nu nagaranchcha asatethaa wolqqay dhayana mala, nu eca asatethaa Kiristtoosanna masqqaliyaa bolla misimaariyan dhishetti kaqetteeddawaa ereetto.  
\v 7 Ayissi gooppe, itti uray hayqqiyaa wode nagaraa wolqqay A mooddenna; shin  
\v 8 nuuni Kiristtoosanna hayqqeeddawaa gidooppe, aananna qassi de7anawaa ammaneetto.  
\v 9 Ayissi gooppe, Kiristtoosi hayquwaappe denddeeddawaa, qassi laa7enthuwaa I hayqqennawaanne hayquu sinthappe A mooddennawaa nuuni ereetto.  
\v 10 I itti kaallakka hayqqeedda; nagaraw A bolla wolqqay baawa; shin I ha de7iyaa de7uwaa Xoossaw de7ee.  
\v 11 Hawaadan qassi hintte nagaraa oothennaadan, hinttentta hayqqeeddawaadan qoppite; shin Godaa Kiristtoosa Yesuusa bagganna Xoossaw hintte paxa de7iyaawaadan, hinttentta qoppite. 
\p  
\v 12 Hewaa diraw, hintte hinttenttu asatethaa amuwaassi azazettana mala, nagaray hayqqiyaa hintte asatethaa mooddoppo.  
\v 13 Qassi hintte asatethaappe itti saanne iita oosuwaa oothanaw nagaraw immoppite; shin hayquwaappe denddeedda asaadan hinttentta Xoossaw immite; qassi hintte kumentha asatethaakka xillo oosuwaa oothanaw Xoossaw immite;  
\v 14 ayissi gooppe, nagaray hinttentta mooddanaw danddayenna; hintte Xoossaa aadho keekatethaa garssanna de7iitappe attin, higgiyaappe garssanna de7ikkita. 
\s1 Xillotethaw Aylle Gidiyaawaa 
\p  
\v 15 Yaatina, waananee? Xoossaa aadho keekatethaa garssanna de7iinoppe attin, higgiyaappe garssanna de7enna diraw, nagaraa oothaanee? Gidenna;  
\v 16 hintte hinttentta itti uraw azazettanaw, aylliyaadan oothiide immiyaa wode, he hinttentta azaziyaawoo aylletuwaa gidiyaawaa eriita; woy hintte hinttenttoo hayquwaa ahiyaa nagaraw eeno giita; woy hintte hinttentta xillo oothiyaa azazoo eeno giita.  
\v 17 Shin Xoossaw galatay gido; ayissi gooppe, nagaraw kase hintte aylle; shin guyyeppe hintte akkeedda timirttiyaa giddon de7iyaa tumatethaw hintte kumentha wozanaappe azazetteeddita.  
\v 18 Hinttenttu nagaraa aylletethaappe kesiide, xillotethaw aylle gideeddita. 
\p  
\v 19 Hinttenttu medhetaan daaburanchcha gidiyaa diraw, taani oossikka geliyaa haasayaa haasayay; hintte kase hintte kumentha asatethaa naaquwaa oothanaw, tunatethawunne naaqoo aylle udiide immeeddita; ha77i hewaadankka hintte kumentha asatethaa geeshshabaa oothanaw, xillotethaw aylle udiide immite. 
\p  
\v 20 Hinttenttu nagaraw aylletiide de7iyaa wode, xillotethay hinttenttoo godaa gidenna.  
\v 21 Hinttentta ha77i yeellayiyaa yewatuwaa he wode ootheeddawaappe ay maaduwaa demmeedditee? Ayissi gooppe, he yewatuwaa wurssethay hayquwaa.  
\v 22 Shin nagaraa aylletethaappe hintte kesiide, Xoossaw eenogeeddita; qassi hintte oothiyaa ubbabaani hinttentta ubbakka aw aathiide immeeddita. Hewe hinttenttoo wore; hewaa wurssethay medhinaa de7uwaa.  
\v 23 Ayissi gooppe, nagaraa gatii hayquwaa. Shin Xoossay nu Godaa Kiristtoosa Yesuusa bagganna immiyaa imotay medhinaa de7uwaa. 
\c 7  
\s1 Muse Higgiyaa Qashuwaappe Bilettiyaawaa 
\p  
\v 1 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, hinttenttu ubbay higgiyaa eriyaa diraw, taani giyaawaa loythi eriita; higgii itti asay paxa de7eedda wode xalalaan A mooddee.  
\v 2 Ayissi gooppe, asinaa geleedda mishiratta izi asinay paxa de7eedda keenan, higgiyan aananna qashetta uttaaddu; shin izi asinay hayqqooppe, aananna caaqqeedda higgii izo mooddenna.  
\v 3 Hewaa diraw, iza bare asinay paxa de7ishshin, hara attumawaa gelooppe, asay izo, “Woshummewunno” gaana. Shin izi asinay hayqqooppe, higgii izo mooddenna; iza hara asinaa gelooppenne izo ooninne, “Woshummewunno” geenna. 
\p  
\v 4 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, hewaadan hinttenttu qassi Kiristtoosa asatethaappe itti bagga gidiyaa diraw, hinttenttu aabagganna hayqqeeddita. Qassi nuuni Xoossaa maaddiyaa oosuwaa oothana mala, hinttenttu Xoossay hayquwaappe dentheedda Kiristtoosawantta.  
\v 5 Ayissi gooppe, nuuni nu asatethay koyyeeddawaadan de7iyaa wode, higgii nuuni nagaraa oothanaadan, nuuna denthethee; nu asatethaa giddon iita amuu de7iyaa diraw, nuuni hayqoo ayfiyaa ayfeeddo.  
\v 6 Shin ha77i nuuni nuuna qachcheeddawoo hayqqeedda diraw, Xoossay nuuna higgiyaa qashuwaappe billeedda. Hewaa diraw, nuuni Geeshsha Ayyaanay giigisseedda ooratha ogiyaan Xoossaw eeno gaanawaappe attin, xaafetteedda higgii nuussi giigisseedda eca ogiyaan eeno gookko. 
\s1 Higgiyaanne Nagaraa 
\p  
\v 7 Yaatina, nuuni waaganee? Higgii bare huuphew nagaree? Hewaa gidenna; shin higgii nagaray ayentto taana erisseedda. Ayissi gooppe, taani higgii, “Asaabaa amottoppa” gibeennentto, asaabaa amottiyaawe ayentto erikke. \x - \xo 7:7 \xt Kes 20:17\x* 
\v 8 Shin nagaray taani ubbabaa amottana mala, azazuwaa bagganna ta bolla ogiyaa demmeedda; ayissi gooppe, higgii baawentto, nagaraw wolqqay baawa. 
\p  
\v 9 Kase higgii baynna wode taani paxa; shin azazuu yeedda wode nagaray de7oo simmina,  
\v 10 taani qassi hayqqaaddi; taana paxa wothanaw Xoossay qoppeedda azazuu, taw hayquwaa aheedda.  
\v 11 Ayissi gooppe, nagaray azazuwaa bagganna taana cimmiyaa ogiyaa demmiide, he azazuwan taana wodheedda. \x - \xo 7:11 \xt Dom 3:13\x* 
\p  
\v 12 Hewaa diraw, higgii geeshsha; azazuukka geeshsha, xillanne lo77a. 
\p  
\v 13 Yaatina, lo77obay taw hayquwaa aheeddee? Hewaa gidenna; shin taw hewaa nagaray aheedda; asay nagaray ayentto shaakkiide erana mala, nagaray lo77obaa bagganna, taw hayquwaa aheedda. Qassi azazuu, “Ooninne nagaraa oothanaw bessenna” yaagiyaa diraw, nagaray kasewaappe aadhdhi iiteedda. 
\s1 Asaa De7uwaa Garssan De7iyaa Baaxiyaa 
\p  
\v 14 Nuuni higgii Xoossawaa gidiyaawaa ereetto; shin taani taana nagaraw zali77eedda hayqqiyaa asa;  
\v 15 taani oothiyaawaa wozanaa aathikke; ayissi gooppe, taani ixxiyaawaa oothayppe attin, taani oothanaw dosiyaawaa oothikke.\x - \xo 7:15 \xt Gal 5:17\x* 
\v 16 Taani ixxiyaawaa oothiyaawaa gidooppe, higgii lo77a gidiyaawaa markkattay.  
\v 17 Hewaa gidooppe, he yewuwaa ta bolla de7iyaa nagaray oothiyaawaappe attin, ha77i taani oothikke. 
\p  
\v 18 Taanan, hewenne ta asatethaan lo77obay de7ennawaa taani eray; ayissi gooppe, lo77obaa oothiyaa amuu ta bolla de7ooppekka, taani he lo77obaa oothananaw danddayikke.  
\v 19 Taani ixxiyaa iitabaa oothayppe attin, taani dosiyaa lo77obaa oothikke.  
\v 20 Shin taani ixxiyaawaa oothiyaawaa gidooppe, hewaa ta bolla de7iyaa nagaray oothiyaawaappe attin, ha77i hewaa oothiyaawe taana gidikke. 
\p  
\v 21 Simmi taani lo77obaa oothanaw dosishshin, iitabaa oothiyaawe taw higge gidiyaawaa demmaaddi.  
\v 22 Ayissi gooppe, taani ta wozanaa giddon Xoossaa higgiyan nashettay;  
\v 23 shin ta bollaa giddon de7iyaa ta wozanaa qofaa higgiyaanna wadhettiyaa dumma higgiyaa be7ay. He higgii ta bollaa giddon de7iyaa nagaraa oosissiyaa higgiyan taana qashissee.  
\v 24 Taani ayba nashechchi baynna asee! Taana hayqoo afiyaa ha asatethaappe ashshanawe oonee?  
\v 25 Nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa bagganna Xoossaw galatay gido. 
\p Simmi taani ta wozanaa qofaan Xoossaa higgew eeno gay. Shin ta asatethaan taana nagaraa oosissiyaa higgew eeno gay. 
\c 8  
\s1 Geeshsha Ayyaanay Koyyiyaawaadan De7ussaa 
\p  
\v 1 Hewaa diraw, Kiristtoosa Yesuusanna de7iyaawanttu bollan pirdday ha77i baawa;  
\v 2 ayissi gooppe, Kiristtoosa Yesuusa bagganna nuussi de7uwaa immiyaa Geeshsha Ayyaanaa higgii taana \f + \fr 8:2 \fq taana: \ft Itti itti Geeshsha Qaalaa bilethay, neena woy hinttentta yaagee; haray qay nuuna yaagee.\f* nagaraa higgiyaa aylletethaappenne hayquwaa higgiyaa aylletethaappe kesseedda.  
\v 3 Asaa asatethay daaburanchcha gidiyaa diraw, higgii oothanaw danddayibeennawaa Xoossay ootheedda; nagaranchchatuwaa asatethaa mala asatethaanna de7iyaa bare Na7aa, asay ootheedda nagaraw yarshshuwaa gidanaw Xoossay kiittiide, asaa asatethaa giddon de7iyaa nagaraa pirddeedda.  
\v 4 Geeshsha Ayyaanay koyyiyaawaadan de7iyaawanttuppe attin, nu asatethay koyyiyaawaadan de7anawanttu bolla, nu bolla, higgiyaa xillo azazuu polettana mala, Xoossay hawaa ootheedda. 
\p  
\v 5 Barenttu asatethay koyyiyaawaadan de7iyaawanttu barenttu asatethaabaa qoppiino; shin Geeshsha Ayyaanay koyyiyaawaadan de7iyaawanttu Geeshsha Ayyaanaabaa qooppiino.  
\v 6 Asatethaabaa qoppussay hayquwaa ahee; shin Geeshsha Ayyaanaabaa qoppussay de7uwaanne sarotethaa ahee.  
\v 7 Asatethaabaa qoppussay Xoossaw ixo; ayaw gooppe, asatethay Xoossaa higgew eeno geenna; qassi eeno gaanawukka aw danddayettenna.  
\v 8 Barenttu asatethaw eeno giyaawanttu Xoossaa nashechchanaw danddaykkino. 
\p  
\v 9 Shin Xoossaa Ayyaanay hinttenttun de7ooppe, Geeshsha Ayyaanay giyaawaadan de7iitappe attin, hintte asatethay koyyiyaawaadan de7ikkita. Shin ooninne Kiristtoosa Ayyaanay baynnawaa gidooppe, he uray Kiristtoosawaa gidenna.  
\v 10 Shin Kiristtoosi hinttenttun de7ooppe, hintte asatethay nagaraa gaasuwan hayqqeeddawaa; shin hintte ayyaanay xillotethaa gaasuwan hinttenttun paxa de7ee.  
\v 11 Shin Yesuusa hayquwaappe dentheedda Xoossaa Ayyaanay hintte giddon de7ooppe, hayquwaappe Kiristtoosa dentheedda Xoossay qassi hinttenttun de7iyaa bare Geeshsha Ayyaanaan, hayqqiyaa hintte asatethawukka de7uwaa immana. 
\p  
\v 12 Simmi taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, nuuni acuwaanna de7eetto; nu asatethay koyyiyaawaadan de7anaw nuussi bessenna.  
\v 13 Ayissi gooppe, hintte hintte asatethay giyaawaadan de7ooppe, hintte hayqqana; shin hintte hintte nagaraa oosuwaa Geeshsha Ayyaanan wodhooppe, paxa de7ana.  
\v 14 Xoossaa Ayyaanay kaalethiyaa ubbatuu Xoossaa naanaa.  
\v 15 Ayissi gooppe, nuuni nu kooshshaa dhoqqu oothiide, “Abbaa! Ta Aabboo” yaagiide xeesiyaa, nuuna Xoossaa naanaa kessiyaa Geeshsha Ayyaanaa Xoossaappe akkeeddoppe attin, laa7ethuwaa yayyanaw aylle kessiyaa ayyaanaa akkibeykko.  
\v 16 Xoossaa Ayyaanay bare huuphew nu ayyaanaanna gidiide, nuuni Xoossaa naanaa gidiyaawaa markkattee.  
\v 17 Nuuni A naanaa gidooppe, I bare asaw minjjeedda anjjuwaa laattana; qassi nuuni Xoossay Kiristtoosaw minjjeeddawaakka aananna laattana; nuuni Kiristtoosa waayyiyaa aananna shaakkooppe, A bonchchuwaakka aananna shaakkana. 
\s1 Xoossaa Naanaw Qonccanaw De7iyaa Bonchchuwaa 
\p  
\v 18 Ayissi gooppe, nuuni ha77i waayyettiyaa waayyiyaa nuussi sinthappe qonccana bonchchuwaanna gathanaw, ubbakka danddayettenna gaade taani qoppay.  
\v 19 Xoossay medhdheedda medhetaa ubbay Xoossaa naanay qonccanawaa loythi laamoti utteedda.  
\v 20 Ayissi gooppe, medhetaa ubbay maaduu baynnabaa gidanaadan, Xoossay A bolla pirddeedda; sinthappe demmana giide nashechchaan naagi uttanaadan udeedda Xoossay koyyeedda diraw haneeddappe attin, medhetaa ubbay bare huuphew koyyeeddawaan gidenna.  
\v 21 Medhetaa ubbay bare huuphew bashshaa aylletethaappe itti gallassi kesanawaa; qassi he medhetatuu Xoossaa naanay aylletethaappe keseedda bonchcho kessaa shaakkana.  
\v 22 Ayissi gooppe, medhetaa ubbay ittippe hawaa gakkanaw, macca asaa yeluu oyqqina ooliyaawaadan, sakuwan ooliyaawaa nuuni ereetto.  
\v 23 Qassi hewaa xalalaa gidenna; nuuni, Geeshsha Ayyaanaa Xoossaa bayra imotaadaan udiide akkeeddawanttu, nu huuphew qassi Xoossay nuuna bare naanaa oothanaadaninne nu kumentha asatethaa wozanaadan naagiidde, nu giddon ooleetto.  
\v 24 Ayissi gooppe, nuuni Xoossay immana geeddawaan atteeddo. Shin nuuni Xoossay immana geeddawaa be7ooppe, yaatina, hewe nashechchaan naagiyaawaa gidenna; ayissi gooppe, bare be7iyaawaa demmana giidde, nashechchaan naagiyaawe oonee?  
\v 25 Shin nuuni be7ennawaa demmana giide, nashechchaan naagooppe, hewaa danddayiide naageetto. 
\p  
\v 26 Hawaadan qassi Geeshsha Ayyaanay nu daaburaa maaddanaw yee; ayissi gooppe, nuuni Xoossaa wooti woossanaw bessintto erokko; shin Geeshsha Ayyaanay bare huuphew qaalaan qonccissanaw danddayettenna ooliyan nuussi gaannatee.  
\v 27 Qassi asaa wozanaa biddiyaa Xoossay, Geeshsha Ayyaanay I koyyiyaawaadan, Xoossaa naatoo gaannatiyaa diraw, Geeshsha Ayyaanaa qofay ayentto eree. 
\p  
\v 28 Xoossay barena siiqiyaawanttoo, bare qofaadan xeeseeddawanttoo, ubba yewuwaa lo77otethaw oothiyaawaa nuuni ereetto.  
\v 29 Xoossay bare Na7ay cora ishatuwaa giddon bayra gidanaadan, I kase ereeddawantta qassi bare Na7aa malatanaadan, kasetiide qofaa qachcheedda.  
\v 30 Xoossay kasetiide qoppeeddawantta, unttuntta qassi xeeseedda; he xeeseeddawanttakka geeshsheedda; he geeshsheeddawanttakka qassi bonchcheedda. 
\s1 Xoossaa Siiquwaa 
\p  
\v 31 Yaatina, nuuni hawaa ubbaa waaganee? Xoossay nu bagga gidooppe, nuuna ooni eqettanawe?  
\v 32 I haray atto bare Na7aakka waayyiyaappe guyye ashshibeenna; shin A nuussi ubbaw aathiide immi aggeedda. I bare Na7aa immeeddawe qassi nuussi ubbabaa coo immennee? 
\p  
\v 33 Xoossay dooreeddawantta oonee mootanawe? Xoossay bare huuphew unttuntta xillisseedda.  
\v 34 Yaatina, unttunttu bolla pirddanaw danddayiyaawe oonee? Hewaa gooppe, hayquwaappe denddiide, Xoossaappe ushechcha bagganna utteedda, Kiristtoosi Yesuusa; I qassi nuussi gaannatee. 
\p  
\v 35 Simmi nuuna Kiristtoosa siiquwaappe shaakkanawe oonee? Waayyii woy metuu woy yederssuu woy koshay woy kalluu woy yashshay woy olay nuuna shaakkanee?  
\v 36 Xoossaa Maxaafay, “Nuuni ne diraw, ubba gallassi hayqqeetto; shukaw afiyaa dorssaadan paydetteetto” yaagee. \x - \xo 8:36 \xt Maz 44:22\x* 
\v 37 Shin nuuni nuuna siiqeedda aani ha yewuwaa ubbaan nuuna xooniyaawanttuppe aadhdheetto. 
\p  
\v 38-39 Ayissi gooppe, hayquwaa gidina, de7uwaa, kiitanchchatuwaa gidina, mooddiyaawantta, ha77i de7iyaawantta gidina, sinthappe yaanawaa, wolqqaamatuwaa gidina, bolla saluwaa gidina, garssa sa7aa, ay medhetaa gidinakka, nu Godaa Kiristtoosa Yesuusan de7iyaa Xoossaa siiquwaappe nuuna shaakkanaw danddayennawaa taani eraaddi. 
\c 9  
\s1 Xoossay Kase Dooreedda Israa7eeliyaa Asaa 
\p  
\v 1 Taani tumuwaa haasayay; taani Kiristtoosassa; qassi worddotikke. Geeshsha Ayyaanay mooddiyaa ta tilla wozanay taani worddotennawaa taw markkattee.  
\v 2-3 Taw ashuwan zare gidiyaa taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, ta wozanaan daro qaretaynne aggenna qofay de7ee. Ayissi gooppe, taani ta huuphew unttunttu diraw, Xoossaa sheqaappe garssanna de7aarikkitaashsha! Qassi Kiristtoosappekka shaakettaarikkitaashshaa!  
\v 4 Unttunttu Israa7eeliyaa asatuwaa; Xoossay unttuntta bare naanaa udiide, bare bonchchuwaa unttunttunna shaakkeedda. Unttunttunna qaalaa geliide, higgiyaa unttunttoo immeedda. Unttunttu Xoossaw bessiyaa ogiyaan goyinniino; qassi Xoossay immana geeddawaakka akkeeddino. \x - \xo 9:4 \xt Kes 4:22\x* 
\v 5 Unttunttu zerethaani kase aawatuwa zare; qassi Kiristtoosikka ashuwan unttunttu zare. I, ubbaappe bolla gidiide mooddiyaa, medhinaw galatetteeddawe Xoossaa. Amen77i. 
\p  
\v 6 Shin taani, “Xoossay immana geeddawe attana” yaagikke. Ayissi gooppe, Israa7eeliyaa asaa ubbatuu Xoossay dooreeddawantta gidikkino.  
\v 7 Qassi Abraahaame zerethatuu ubbatuu Xoossaa naanaa gidikkino. Xoossay Abraahaamossi, “Ne zerethay Yisaaqa bagganna xeesettanawaa” yaageedda. \x - \xo 9:7 \xt Dom 21:12\x* 
\v 8 Hewaa guussay unttunttu Xoossay immana geedda ogiyaan yeletteedda naanay zariyaadan paydettana; shin asaa qofaadan yeletteeddawanttu Xoossaa naanaa gidikkino guussaa.  
\v 9 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay immana giide haasayeeddawe hawaa; “Taani ha geetetteeddawaadan hewode yaana; Saarakka attuma na7aa yelana” yaageedda. \x - \xo 9:9 \xt Dom 18:10\x* 
\p  
\v 10 Hewaa xalalaakka gidenna; Irbbiqa yeleedda mantte naanaa aawuu ittuwaa; ikka nu aawuwaa Yisaaqa.  
\v 11-12 Shin itti na7aa dooreedda Xoossay bare huuphew qoppeeddawaa gidanaadan, Xoossay Irbbiqiw, “Bayray teefaw azazettana” yaageedda; I hewaa unttunttu yelettanaappenne iitabaa woy lo77obaa aynne oothanaappe kasenna geedda. Hewaa diraw, Xoossaa dooruu A xeeseeddawaadanippe attin, unttunttu ootheeddawaana gidenna. \x - \xo 9:11-12 \xt Dom 25:33\x* 
\v 13 Xoossaa Maxaafay, “Yayiqooba siiqaaddi; shin Eesaa ixxaaddi” yaagee. 
\p  
\v 14 Yaatina, nuuni waaganee? Xoossay deshissiide pirddii? Hewaa gidenna.  
\v 15 Ayissi gooppe, Musew I, 
\q1 “Taani maaranaw koyyiyaawantta maarana; 
\q2 qassi qarettanaw koyyiyaawanttussikka qarettana” 
\m yaageedda. \x - \xo 9:15 \xt Kes 33:19\x* 
\v 16 Simmi Xoossay asaa maariyaawe I maaranaw koyyiyaa diraassappe attin, asay koyyiyaa woy oothiyaa diraassa gidenna. 
\p  
\v 17 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa Maxaafay Gibxe kaatiyaassi, “Taani ta wolqqaa neenan bessanawunne ta sunthay alamiyaa ubbaan odettanaw, hewaassi taani neena kawuthaaddi” yaagee. \x - \xo 9:17 \xt Kes 9:16\x* 
\v 18 Simmi Xoossay maarana koyyiyaawaa maaree; qassi wozanaa gorddana koyyiyaawaa wozanaa gorddee. 
\s1 Xoossaa Hanqquwaanne Maarotaa 
\p  
\v 19 Simmi hintte taana, “Hewe tuma gidooppe, Xoossay asaa bayizzuwaassi ayaw toshii? Xoossay geeddawaa ixxaaddi gaanawe oonee?” yaaganaw danddayiita. 
\p  
\v 20 Shin ta laggew, Xoossaassi zaaranaw neeni oonee? Urqqaappe medhetteedda miishshay guyye zaariide barena medhdheeddawaa, “Taana hawaadan ayissi medhdhaaddii?” giide oochchanaw dandday? \x - \xo 9:20 \xt Isa 29:16; 45:9\x* 
\v 21 Woy urqqaa medhdhiyaawe bare medhdhiyaa urqqaa bare koyyiyaawaadan oothanawunne itti mala urqqaappe ittuwaa bonchcho miishshaa udiide, qassi ittuwaa tooshetteedda oosuwaa oothiyaa miishshaa udiide medhdhanaw aw maati baawee? 
\p  
\v 22 Xoossay ootheeddawe hawaanna ittuwaa. I bare hanqquwaa bessanawunne bare wolqqaa erissanaw koyyeedda; I bare hanqquwan pirddanawantta, bayizzanaw giigi utteeddawantta, daro genccuwan danddayeedda.  
\v 23 Qassi I maareeddawanttoo, bare bonchchuwaa akkanaw giigissi wotheeddawanttussi I ay keenaa bonchchettinttonne bessanaw koyyeedda.  
\v 24 Nuuni I xeeseeddawantta; shin Ayihuda asaa xalalaappe gidennaan, Ayihuda gidenna asaa giddoppekka xeeseedda. 
\p  
\v 25 Hoose7a maxaafan I giyaawe hawaa; 
\q2 “Ta asaa gidennawantta, 
\q2 ‘Ta asa’ gaade xeesana. 
\q2 Taani siiqabeenna zariyaakka, 
\q2 ‘Ta siiqaatoo’ gaade xeesana. \x - \xo 9:25 \xt Hos 2:23\x* 
\q1  
\v 26 ‘Hinttenttu ta asaa gidikkita’ giyaawaa 
\q2 unttunttu siseedda he sa7aan, 
\q2 unttunttu, ‘De7uwaa Xoossaa naanaa’ geetettiide xeesettanawantta” 
\m yaagee. \x - \xo 9:26 \xt Hos 1:10\x* 
\v 27 Isiyaasi Israa7eeliyaa asaabaa yaagiide haasayeedda; 
\q2 “Israa7eeliyaa asay abbaa matan 
\q2 de7iyaa shafiyaa keena gidooppekka, 
\q1 unttunttuppe amareeddawanttu xalalay attana. \x - \xo 9:27 \xt Isa 10:22-23\x* 
\q1  
\v 28 Ayissi gooppe, Goday sa7aa bollan 
\q1 de7iyaa asaa ubbaa bolla 
\q2 ellekka pirddana” 
\m yaageedda.  
\v 29 Isiyaasi kasetiide, 
\q2 “Ubbaappe Wolqqaama Goday nuussi 
\q2 amareedda zerethaa ashshennentto, 
\q2 nuuni Sodoomaa katamaadaaninne 
\q2 Gamooraa katamaadan haneeddoshshin” 
\m yaagi haasayeedda. \x - \xo 9:29 \xt Isa 1:9\x* 
\p  
\v 30 Yaatina, nuuni waaganee? Xillotethaa koyyibeenna Ayihuda gidenna asay ammanuwan xilleedda;  
\v 31 shin Israa7eeliyaa asay barentta xillissiyaa higgiyaa koyyeeddawanttu he higgiyaa demmibeykkino.  
\v 32-33 Ayissi demmibeykkinoo? Unttunttu oosuwaanappe attin, ammanuwan xillotethaa koyyibeenna diraassa. Unttunttu Xoossaa Maxaafay, 
\q1 “Akeekite; taani Xiyoonen asaa dhubbiyaa shuchchaa, 
\q2 unttunttu ogiyaan zaallaa wothana. 
\q1 Shin aani ammaniyaa ooninne yeellatenna” 
\m yaagiide xaafettowaadan dhubbiyaa shuchchan dhubetteeddino. \x - \xo 9:32-33 \xt Isa 28:16\x* 
\c 10  
\s1 Israa7eeliyaa Asay Xoossaa Ogiyaa Kaallibeenna 
\p  
\v 1 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, taani Israa7eeliyaa asaw ta kumentha wozanaappe amottiyaawenne Xoossaa woossiyaawe unttunttu attanaassa;  
\v 2 ayissi gooppe, unttunttu Xoossaw oothanaw loythi koyyiyaawaa taani markkattay; shin unttunttu Xoossaw oothanaw loythi koyyiyaa koshshay tumu eratethaappe gidenna.  
\v 3 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay asaa xillissiyaa ogiyaa unttunttu erennaan, barenttu huuphe xillotethaa essanaw koyyeeddino; qassi barenttu huuphew Xoossay asaa xillissiyaa ogew eeno gibeykkino.  
\v 4 Ayissi gooppe, ammaneedda ubbay xillanaadan, Kiristtoosi higgiyaa qofaa poleedda. 
\s1 Atotethay Ubbaassa 
\p  
\v 5 Asay higgew azazettiide xilliyaabaw Muse, “Higgii azaziyaawaa oothiyaa ooninne he higgiyan paxa de7ana” yaagi xaafeedda; \x - \xo 10:5 \xt Wog 18:5\x* 
\v 6 shin ammanuwan xilliyaabaw geetetteeddawe hawaa; “Ne wozanaan, ‘Ooni saluwaa pude baanee?’ goppa. Hewe Kiristtoosa duge wothanaassa; \x - \xo 10:6 \xt Zar 30:12-14\x* 
\v 7 woy ‘Duge sa7aa garssa wodhdhanawe oonee?’ gooppa. Hewe Kiristtoosa hayquwaappe denthanaassa.  
\v 8 Shin I giyaawe hawaa; ‘Xoossaa qaalay ne mataana; ne doonaaninne ne wozanaan de7ee’ geetetteedda” yaagee. Hewekka nuuni hinttenttoo odiyaa ammanuwaa qaalaa. 
\p  
\v 9 Neeni, “Yesuusi Godaa” gaade ne doonaan markkattooppe, qassi Xoossay hayquwaappe A dentheeddawaa ne wozanaan ammanooppe, neeni attana.  
\v 10 Ayissi gooppe, asay bare wozanaan ammaniide xillee; bare doonankka markkattiide attee.  
\v 11 Xoossaa Maxaafay, “Aani ammaniyaa ooninne yeellatenna” yaagee. \x - \xo 10:11 \xt Isa 28:16\x* 
\v 12 Ayihuda asaanne Ayihuda gidenna asaa giddon dummatethay baawa. Itti Xoossay ubbaa Godaa; I barena xeesiyaa ubbatoo daro keeka.  
\v 13 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa Maxaafay, “Godaa sunthaa xeesiyaa ooninne attana” yaagee. \x - \xo 10:13 \xt Iyu 2:32\x* 
\p  
\v 14 Yaatina, unttunttu A ammanibeennawantta gidooppe, wooti A xeesanaw danddayiinoo? Qassi qaalaa sisibeennawanttu waani ammananaw danddayiinoo? Qaalaa odiyaawe dhayooppe, unttunttu waani sisanaw danddayiinoo?  
\v 15 Qassi qaalaa odiyaawanttu kiitettennan aggooppe, oosuu wooti odettanaw danddayii? Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa Maxaafay, “Nashechchiyaa mishiraachchuwaa odiyaawanttu yuussay wooti lo77ii!” yaagee. \x - \xo 10:15 \xt Isa 52:7\x* 
\p  
\v 16 Shin unttunttu ubbay wonggalaw azazettibeykkino; ayissi gooppe Isiyaasi, “Ta Godaw, nuuni markkatteeddawaa ooni ammaneeddee?” yaageedda. \x - \xo 10:16 \xt Isa 53:1\x* 
\v 17 Simmi asay qaalaa sisiide ammanee; qassi itti uray Kiristtoosa qaalaa, odina sisee. 
\p  
\v 18 Shin unttunttu qaalaa sisibeennawe tumee gaade taani oochchay. Tuma unttunttu siseeddino; Xoossaa Maxaafay, 
\q1 “Unttunttu haasayaa kooshshay 
\q2 sa7aa ubbaan laaletteedda; 
\q1 unttunttu qaalaykka sa7aa gaxaa gakkeedda” 
\m yaageedda. \x - \xo 10:18 \xt Maz 19:4\x* 
\v 19 Shin Israa7eeliyaa asatuu eribeykkinoyee gaade taani oochchay. Muse kase, 
\q1 “Taani hinttentta asa gidenna asatuwan seelissana; 
\q2 qassi eeya asatuwan taani hinttentta hanqqethissana” 
\m yaageedda. \x - \xo 10:19 \xt Zar 32:21\x* 
\v 20 Qassi Isiyaasi daro xaliide, 
\q1 “Taana koyyibeennawanttoo beettaaddi; 
\q2 taana oochchibeennawanttookka qonccaaddi” 
\m yaagee. \x - \xo 10:20 \xt Isa 65:1\x* 
\v 21 Shin Israa7eelatuwabaa I haasayiidde, 
\q1 “Gallassaa ubbaa azazettennawanttoonne 
\q2 tawaa ixxiyaawanttoo ta kushiyaa miccaaddi” 
\m yaagee. \x - \xo 10:21 \xt Isa 65:2\x* 
\c 11  
\s1 Xoossay Israa7eeliyaa Asaa Wurssi Olibeenna 
\p  
\v 1 Yaatina, Xoossay bare asaa ixxeedde gaade oochchoo? Hewaa gidenna; ayissi gooppe, taani ta huuphew Israa7eeliyaa asa; Abraahaame zare; Biiniyaama yaraa.  
\v 2 Xoossay koyro dooreedda bare asatuwaa ixxenna; Xoossaa Maxaafay, Eelaasa taarikiyaa giddon, Eelaasi Israa7eelatuwaa Xoossaa sinthan wooti mootintto, hintte eriita.  
\v 3 “Godaw, unttunttu he sunthan nabatuwaa wodheeddino; ne yarshshiyaasaakka koleeddino. Yaatina, taani ta xalalay attaaddi. Qassi unttunttu taanakka wodhanaw koyyiino” yaageedda. \x - \xo 11:3 \xt 1Ka 19:10,14\x* 
\p  
\v 4 Xoossay aw waagi zaareeddee? “Taani Eeqaa Ba7aalaw gulbbatibeenna laappu sha77a asaa taw ashshaaddi” yaageedda. \x - \xo 11:4 \xt 1Ka 19:18\x* 
\p  
\v 5 Hawaadankka qassi ha wodiyaan, Xoossay bare aadho keekatethaan dooreedda amareedda asatuu de7iino.  
\v 6 Shin I bare aadho keekatethaan dooreeddappe attin, unttunttu oosuwan unttuntta dooribeenna; hewe dhayooppe, A aadho keekatethay tumu aadho keekatetha gidenna. 
\p  
\v 7 Yaatina, ayee? Israa7eeliyaa asatuu barenttu koyyiyaawaa demmibeykkino; shin Xoossay dooreedda amareeddawanttu demmeeddino. Yokkonttu wozanay minneedda.  
\v 8 Hawaadankka, Xoossaa Maxaafay, 
\q2 “Xoossay unttunttu barenttu ayfiyaan be7ennaadaaninne 
\q2 barenttu haythaan sisennaadan, 
\q2 hawaa gakkanaw unttunttoo 
\q2 azalla ayyaanaa immeedda” 
\m yaageedda. \x - \xo 11:8 \xt Zar 29:4; Isa 29:10\x* 
\v 9 Qassi Daawite yaageedda; 
\q2 “Unttunttu miyaa gaytay unttuntta phiriyaadan oyqqo; 
\q2 unttuntta guufantho; unttunttoo kushiyaa shiri ciggo. \x - \xo 11:9 \xt Maz 69:22-23\x* 
\q1  
\v 10 Unttunttu xeellennaadan, unttunttu ayfii goozetto; 
\q1 ubba wode barenttu metuwan quunniide de7iino” 
\m yaageedda. 
\p  
\v 11 Yaatina, Ayihudatuu dhubetteedda wode, denddennaadan kunddeeddino? Hewaa gidenna; unttunttu nagaraa ootheedda diraw, atotethay unttunttu Ayihuda gidenna asatuwaa qanaatanaadan, Ayihuda gidenna asaw yeedda.  
\v 12 Shin Ayihudatuu nagaraa ootheedda diraw, alamew daro anjjuu yeedda; qassi unttunttu kunddethaykka Ayihuda gidenna asaw daro anjjuwaa aheedda. Yaatina, Ayihudatuu ubbay gujettiyaa wode, anjjuu woysa keena daranddeeshsha! 
\s1 Ayihuda Gidenna Asay Attana Atotethaa 
\p  
\v 13 Shin taani ha77i hinttenttoo, Ayihuda gidenna asaw haasayay; taani Ayihuda gidenna asaw Yesuusi kiitteeddawaa gidiyaa diraw, ta oosuwaa bonchchana.  
\v 14 Taani ta zare gidiyaa asatuwaa qanatanchchatuwaa udooppe, ooni eri unttunttuppe amareeddawantta ashshennaan aggikke.  
\v 15 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay unttuntta ixxeedda wode, ha alami Xoossaanna sigetteedda. Yaatina Xoossay unttuntta shiishshi akkiya wode, hayqqeeddawe de7uwaa demmanaappe attin, ayee hananee? 
\p  
\v 16 Koyro ayfe bagga munaqay anjjetteeddawaa gidooppe, muume munaqaykka qassi anjjetteeddawaa gidana; itti mithaa xaphuu anjjetteeddawaa gidooppe, haythay ubbaykka qassi anjjetteeddawaa gidana.  
\v 17 Shin woraan doleedda wogaraa mithaa qankkaappe ittuwaa ittuwaa kareeddasaan, neena woraan doleedda wogaraa mithaa malaa he wogaraanna gathi qachcheeddo; neeni qassi zaytii kesiyaa wogaraa mithaa xaphuwaanna ittippe de7aa.  
\v 18 Simmi neeni he karetti wodhdheedda qankkatuwaa bollan otorettanaw bessenna; shin neeni otorettiyaawaa gidooppekka, xaphuu neena tookkeeppe attin, neeni xaphuwaa tookkennawaa akeeka. 
\p  
\v 19 Hewaa diraw neeni, “E; shin qankkatuu taani unttunttu sa7aan gelanaadan karetteeddino” yaagana.  
\v 20 Hewe tuma; unttunttu ammanibeenna diraw, karetteeddino; neeni ammaneedda diraw, he sa7aan eqqaadda. Shin yayyappe attin, otoro qofaa qoppoppa.  
\v 21 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay medhetaa qankkaa malatiyaawanttoo, Ayihudatoo qarettibeennawaa gidooppe, new qarettiyaawaa malatii? 
\p  
\v 22 Simmi Xoossaa keekatethaanne xalatethaa be7a. Kunddeeddawanttoo I xalaa; shin neeni A keekatethaani minnaade de7ooppe, I new keeka; hewe dhayooppe, neenikka qassi karettana.  
\v 23 Ayihudatuukka qassi ammanennaan ixxiyaawaa aggooppe, Xoossay kase unttunttu de7iyaasaan zaariide wothana; ayissi gooppe, I unttuntta zaariide wothanaw danddayee.  
\v 24 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay hinttentta woraan de7iyaa koyro medhetaa wogaraa mithaappe qanxxiide, hinttenttu medhetaan woraan dolowanttudan gidennaan gaden tokkeedda wogaraa mithaanna gathi oytheeddawaa gidooppe, yaatina, he karetti wodhdheedda koyro medhetaa qankkatuwaa zarethiide, unttuntta koyro medhetaan doleedda barenttu wogaraa mithaanna gathi qachchanaw, A ayee xoonanawe? 
\s1 Xoossaa Maarotay Ubbaassa 
\p  
\v 25 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, taani hintte eranaadan koyyiyaa tumu xuuraa yewuu de7ee; hewe hintte hinttentta hinterekka, nuuni aadhdheedda eranchcha yaagiide qoppiyaawaa diggee; Israa7eeliyaa asaappe baggay sisennaan ixxeedda; shin he sisennaan ixxiyaawe Ayihuda gidenna asaa kumentha payduu Xoossaakko gakkanaassi gami77ana.  
\v 26 Hawaadankka, Israa7eeliyaa asay ubbay attana; Xoossaa Maxaafay hawaadan yaagee; 
\q2 “Ashshiyaawe Xiyoone geetettiyaa katamaappe 
\q2 yiide, nagaraa oosuwaa ubbaa Yayiqooba zariyaappe diggana. \x - \xo 11:26 \xt Isa 59:20\x* 
\q1  
\v 27 Taani unttunttu nagaraa atto yaagiyaa wode, 
\q2 unttunttunna gelana qaalaa caaquu hawaa” 
\m yaagee. \x - \xo 11:27 \xt Erm 31:33-34\x* 
\p  
\v 28 Ayihuda gidenna asatoo, Ayihudatuu wonggalaa mishiraachchuwaa bagganna hintte diraw, Xoossaanna morkke; shin Xoossaa dooruwaa bagganna aawatuwa diraw, unttunttu I siiqiyaawantta.  
\v 29 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay bare immeeddawaa guyye akkenna; qassi bare xeeseeddawaa ixxaaddi geenna.  
\v 30 Ayihuda gidennawanttoo, Xoossaw hintte kasenna azazettibeykkita; shin Ayihudatuu azazettennan ixxeedda diraw, Xoossaa maarotethaa ha77i hintte akkeeddita.  
\v 31 Hawaadan, hintte akkeedda maarotethaa diraw, Ayihudatuu qassi Xoossaa maarotethaa ha77i akkanaadan, Xoossaw azazettennan ixxeeddino.  
\v 32 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay asaa ubbaa maarana mala, asay ubbay aw azazettennan ixxiyaa hanotaan qachcheedda. 
\p  
\v 33 Xoossaa duretethay woysa keena daree? A aadho eratethaynne A eratethay woysa keena ciimmee? A pirddaa odanawe oonee? I bare oothiyaawaa ayissi oothintto, oonee akeekiyaawee? \x - \xo 11:33 \xt Isa 55:8\x* 
\v 34 Hewaa Xoossaa Maxaafay, “Godaa wozanaa eriyaawe oonee? A zoranaw danddayiyaawe oonee? \x - \xo 11:34 \xt Isa 40:13\x* 
\v 35 Woy bare kushiyaa zaarana mala, aw ittibaa immeeddawe de7ii?” yaagee. \x - \xo 11:35 \xt Yob 41:11\x* 
\p  
\v 36 Ayissi gooppe, ubbabaa I medhdheedda; qassi ubbabaykka A maataaninne awunne de7ee; Xoossaw medhinaw bonchchuu gido. Amen77i. \x - \xo 11:36 \xt 1Qo 8:6\x* 
\c 12  
\s1 Xoossaw Oothanaadan Nuuni Waaniide De7anaw Bessii? 
\p  
\v 1 Simmi taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, hintte hintte oonatethaa Xoossaa nashechchiyaa de7onne geeshsha yarshshuwaa udiide, Xoossaw shiishshanaadan, taani hinttentta Xoossaa maarotethaan woossay; Xoossaw hintte goyinnanaw bessiyaa tumu ogii hewaa.  
\v 2 Xoossay hintte qofaa ubbanna dummayiide, hinttentta laammoppe attin, ha alamiyaa asaa malatoppite. He wode hintte, Xoossaa shenii, lo77obay, A nashechchiyaabaynne qassi polo gideeddabay ayentto eranita. 
\p  
\v 3 Xoossay taw immeedda aadho keekatethaan taani hinttenttoo oday. Hinttenttu qoppanaw bessiyaawaappe aathiide, otoruwan qoppoppite; hewaa aggiide, wozanaama asaadan qoppite; Xoossay hinttenttoo huuphiyan huuphiyan immeedda ammanuwaa keenan hintte bolla pirddite.  
\v 4 Nu itti bollaa giddon, cora bollaa qommotuu de7iino; he qommotuwaa ubbawukka dumma dumma oosuu de7ee.  
\v 5 Hawaadan, nuuni cora asaa gidooppekka, Kiristtoosa bagganna itti asa. Qassi nuuni itti asatethaa qommotuwaadan, ittu ittuwaanna oyqetti utteeddo.  
\v 6 Xoossay nuussi immeedda aadho keekatethaan dumma dumma imotay de7ee. Nu imotay nabetethaa gidooppe, nuussi de7iyaa ammanuwaa keenaa odanaw bessee.  
\v 7 Haratuwaa maddussaa gidooppe, he oosuwan minnanaw bessee; tamaarissussaa gidooppe, he tamaarissuwan minnanaw bessee.  
\v 8 Hara asatuwaa minissussaa gidooppe, he oosuwan minnanaw bessee. Bare huuphew de7iyaabaappe haratuwassi immiyaa ooninne wozanaappe immo. Maatay de7iyaa uray minissi oothanaw bessee; haratuwassi keekiyaa uray nashechchaan keekanaw bessee. 
\p  
\v 9 Hinttenttu siiquu asaa bessanaw siiqettiyaawaa gidanaw bessenna. Iitabaa ixxite; lo77obaa minissiide oyqqite.  
\v 10 Ittu ittuwaanna ishatuwaadan siiqettite; ittu ittuwaa bonchchiyaawan nashettite.  
\v 11 Minniide oothite; azalloppite; hintte kumentha wozanaappe Godaw oothite. \f + \fr 12:11 \fq kumentha wozanaappe Godaw oothite: \ft Geeshsha ayyaanaani kaalesettiide kiitettiyaawantta gidite.\f* 
\v 12 Xoossay hinttenttoo immana geeddawaan nashettite; waayyiyan genccite. Ubba wode Xoossaa woossite;  
\v 13 Xoossaa asatuwaa koshshiyaaban maaddite; imathaa mokkite. 
\p  
\v 14 Hinttentta yederssiyaawantta anjjite; unttuntta anjjiteppe attin, sheqqoppite.  
\v 15 Nashettiyaawanttunna nashettite; yeekkiyaawanttunnakka yeekkite.  
\v 16 Asaa ubbaw itti mala qofaa qoppite; oothiyaabaan ubbaan hinttentta toochchiide de7iteppe \f + \fr 12:16 \fq hinttentta toochchiide de7ite: \ft Ashikke gidite guussaa.\f* attin, otorettoppite; hinttentta hintterekka aadho eranchcha giide qoppoppite. \x - \xo 12:16 \xt Lem 3:7\x* 
\p  
\v 17 Ooninne hinttenttoo iitabaa oothooppe, he uraw iitabaa oothi zaaroppite; asaa ubbaw lo77obaa oothanaw qoppite.  
\v 18 Asaa ubbaanna sarotethaan de7anaw, hintte bagganna, hinttenttoo danddayetteeddabaa ubbaa oothite.  
\v 19 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, hintte hintte huuphew asaw haluwaa kesoppite. Xoossay haluwaa kesanaadan, A bolla olite. Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa Maxaafay, 
\q1 “Goday, ‘Taani haluwaa kesana; 
\q2 taani kushiyaa ciggana’ gee” 
\m yaagee. \x - \xo 12:19 \xt Zar 32:35\x* 
\p  
\v 20 Shin Xoossaa Maxaafay, 
\q1 “Ne morkkii koshattooppe, miza. 
\q2 Saamettooppe, ushsha. 
\q1 Ayissi gooppe, neeni hewaa oothiyaawaan 
\q2 A darissa yeellayaasa” 
\m yaagee. \x - \xo 12:20 \xt Lem 25:21-22\x* 
\p  
\v 21 Iitabaa lo77obaan xoonappe attin, iitabay neena xoonoppo. 
\c 13  
\s1 Gadiyaa Ayissiyaawanttussi Eeno Gaanaw Bessee 
\p  
\v 1 Asay ubbay gadiyaa ayissiyaawanttussi eeno gaanaw bessee; ayissi gooppe, Xoossay geennaan de7ishshin, gadiyaa ayissiyaawe de7anaw danddayenna. Ha77i de7iyaa ayissiyaawanttukka Xoossay wotheeddawantta.  
\v 2 Hewaa diraw, ha77i de7iyaa ayissiyaawantta ixxiyaa ooninne Xoossaa azazuwaa ixxee; bare bolla pirddaa ahee.  
\v 3 Ayissi gooppe, ayissiyaawanttu iitabaa oothiyaawantta yashshanawaappe attin, lo77obaa oothiyaawantta yashshikkino. Ayissiyaawoo yayyennaan agganaw koyyay? Yaatooppe lo77obaa ootha; I neena galatana.  
\v 4 Ayissi gooppe, I new lo77obaa oothanaw, Xoossaw qooma. Shin neeni iitabaa oothooppe, iitabaa ootheeddawaa I seeriyaa diraw, aw yayya; I Xoossaa qoomaa. Qassi iitabaa oothiyaawanttu bolla Xoossaa hanqquwaa I ahee.  
\v 5 Hewaa diraw, gadiyaa ayissiyaawanttussi eeno giyaawe Xoossaa muraa xalalaassa gidennaan, hinttenttu wozanaa qofaa dirawukka eeno gaanaw bessee. 
\p  
\v 6 Ayissi gooppe, gadiyaa ayissiyaawanttu barenttu oosuwaa oothiyaa wode, Xoossaw oothiyaa diraw, hintte qaraxaa qanxxiyaawe hewaassa.  
\v 7 Ubba asawukka bessiyaawaa immite. Giiraa giiranaw bessiyaawoo giirite; qaraxaa qanxxanaw bessiyaawoo qanxxite; yayyanaw bessiyaawoo yayyite; bonchchuu bessiyaawaa bonchchite. 
\s1 Ittu Ittuwaanna Siiqettite 
\p  
\v 8 Hinttenttu ittu ittuwaanna siiqettanaappe attin, hara acuu O bollaninne de7oppo. Ayissi gooppe, haraa siiqiyaa ooninne higgii giyaawaa poleedda.  
\v 9 “Woshummoppa; wodhoppa; wuu77oppa; asaabaa amottoppa” giyaa azazatuunne hara azazatuu ubbatuu, “Ne shooruwaa ne huuphiyaadan siiqa” giyaa azazuwan kumiino. \x - \xo 13:9 \xt Kes 20:13-15,17; Zar 5:17-19,21; Wog 19:18\x* 
\v 10 Bare shooruwaa siiqiyaa ooninne aw iitabaa oothenna; hewaa diraw, shooruwaa siiqiyaawe higgiyaa ubbaw eeno giyaawaa. 
\p  
\v 11 Gemi77ushuwaappe hintte beegottiyaa saati ha77i gakkeedda diraw, ha wodiyaa akeekite. Ayissi gooppe, nuuni koyro ammaneedda wodiyaappe, nuuni attiyaa wodii ha77i nuukko matatteedda.  
\v 12 Qammay aadhdhanaw hanee; gallassay matatteedda. Simmi nuuni dhumaa oosuwaa aggiide, poo7uwan olettanaw, olaa miishshaa mayyoytte;  
\v 13 gallassi poo7uwan de7iyaa asaadan, ane maara de7oytte. Yethaaninne mathuwan gidoppo; woshummussaaninne woshummanaw kajjeelussaana gidoppo; palumaaninne qanaatiyaan gidoppo.  
\v 14 Shin Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa, olaa miishshaa A mayyite; hintte nagaranchcha asatethay bare wozanaa amuwaa polanaadan, aw qoppoppite. 
\c 14  
\s1 Asaa Bolla Pirddennaan Aggussaa 
\p  
\v 1 Ammanuwan azalliya uraa shiishshi akkite. Shin I bare huuphew qoppiyaabaan aananna palumettoppite.  
\v 2 Itti uraa ammanuu I ayaa miinanne diggenna. Shin ammanuwan azalliya uray gaden mokkeeddabaa xalalaa mee.  
\v 3 Ubbabaa miyaa uray ubbabaa meenna uraa kadhoppo; ubbabaa meenna uraykka ubbabaa miyaa uraa bolla pirddoppo. Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay A shiishshi akkeedda.  
\v 4 Hara asaa qoomaa bolla pirddiyaawe neeni oonee? I kunddina woy denddina bare Godaassa; shin Goday A denthanaw danddayiyaa diraw, I eqqana. 
\p  
\v 5 Itti uray, “Hiqqa gallassay hara gallassatuwappe aadhdhee” yaagiide qoppiyaa wode, haray, “Ubba gallassatuukka itti mala” giide qoppee. Asay ubbay huuphiyan huuphiyan hewaadan ayissi qoppintto akeeko.  
\v 6 Itti gallassaa hara gallassatuwappe aathiide bonchchiya uray Godaa bonchchoo bonchchee; qumaa miyaa uraykka Godaa bonchchoo mee. Ayissi gooppe, I he qumaa diraw, Xoossaa galatee. Qumaa meennawekka Godaa bonchchoo meennaan aggeedda; qassi Xoossaa galatee.  
\v 7 Ayissi gooppe, nuuppe ooninne bare huuphe xalalaw de7enna; qassi ooninne bare huuphe xalalaw hayqqenna.  
\v 8 Nuuni paxa de7ooppe, Godaw de7eetto; qassi hayqqooppekka, Godaw hayqqeetto. Simmi nuuni paxa de7ooppe woy hayqqooppekka Godaassa. 
\p  
\v 9 Hewaa diraw, Kiristtoosi paxa de7iyaawanttoonne hayqqeeddawanttoo Godaa gidanaw hayqqiide, hayquwaappe denddeedda.  
\v 10 Yaatina, neeni ne ishaa bolla ayissi pirdday? Woy neeni ne ishaa ayissi kadhay? Nuuni ubbaykka Xoossaa pirddaa oydiyaa sinthan eqqana.  
\v 11 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa Maxaafay, 
\q1 “ ‘Taani Goday ta de7uwan caaqqay; 
\q2 asay ubbay ta sinthan gulbbatana. 
\q1 Qassi taani Xoossaa gidiyaawaa 
\q2 asay ubbay markkattana’ yaagay” 
\m yaagee. \x - \xo 14:11 \xt Isa 45:23\x* 
\v 12 Simmi nuuni huuphiyan huuphiyan nubaa Xoossaw odana. 
\s1 Nagaraa Oosuwassi Gaasuwaa Gidoppa 
\p  
\v 13 Hewaa diraw, nuuni ittu ittuwa bolla pirddiyaawaa hawaappe sinthaw ane aggoytte. Shin ubbaappe aathiide, hintte ishaa dhubbiyaabaa woy nagaraan oliyaabaa oothennaadan qofaa qachchite.  
\v 14 Taani Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosanna de7iyaawaan, bare huuphew tuna gidiyaabay baynnawaa eraynne akeekay. Shin itti uray ittibaa tuna giide qoppooppe, hewe aw tuna gidee.  
\v 15 Neeni miyaabaa diraw, ne ishaa qohooppe, simmi neeni siiquwan de7akka. Kiristtoosi A diraw hayqqeedda asaa ne miyaa qumaan bayizzoppa.  
\v 16 Simmi neeni lo77obaa giyaawaa asay kadhoppo.  
\v 17 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossaa kawutethay Geeshsha Ayyaanay immiyaa xillotethaa, sarotethaanne nashechchaa gidiyaawaappe attin, muussaanne ushshaa gidenna.  
\v 18 Ayissi gooppe, Kiristtoosaw hawaadan oothiyaa uray ooninne Xoossaa nashechchee; asaykka A galatee. 
\p  
\v 19 Yaatooppe, ane nuuni sarotethaa ahiyaabaanne nuuna ittuwaa ittuwaanna minissiyaabaa ubbaa koyyeetto.  
\v 20 Xoossaa oosuwaa qumaa diraw bayizzoppa. Qumay ubbay geeshsha; shin hara uraa nagaraan yeggiyaawaa muussay iita.  
\v 21 Hewaassi ashuwaa meennaan woy ushshaa ushennaan aggiyaawe woy ne ishaa dhubbiyaabaa ayaanne oothennaan aggiyaawe lo77a. 
\p  
\v 22 Ha yewuwaan ne ammanuwaa neeppenne Xoossaappe gidduwan naaga. Itti uray lo77a giide I ammanetteeddawaa oothiyaa wode, “Taani lo77uwaa oothaaddi” giide bare wozanaani ammanettooppe, he uray tumu anjjetteeddawaa.  
\v 23 Shin I he miyaabaan sidhooppe, A muussay ammanuwaana gidenna diraw, Xoossay A bolla pirddee; qassi ammanuu baynnaan ootheeddawe ayayinneekka nagara. 
\c 15  
\s1 Asaa Nashechchanaw Bessiyaa Ogiyaa 
\p  
\v 1 Nuuni ammanuwan minneeddawanttu daaburanchchatuwaa tookuwaa tookkanaw bessee; nuuni nu xalalaa nashechchanaw bessenna.  
\v 2 Nuuni huuphiyan huuphiyan nu ishaa maaddanaw, ammanuwan A minissanawunne nashechchanaw bessee.  
\v 3 Ayissi gooppe, haray atto Kiristtoosikka barena nashechchibeenna. Shin Xoossaa Maxaafay, “Neena boreeddawanttu boreedda borii ta bolla wodhdheedda” geeddawaadan haneedda. \x - \xo 15:3 \xt Maz 69:9\x* 
\v 4 Xoossaa Maxaafay nuussi immiyaa genccaaninne minotaan nuuni demmana giide nashechchaan naagi utteeddawe de7ana mala, Xoossaa Maxaafan xaafetteedda ubbabay nuuna tamaarssanaw xaafetteedda. 
\p  
\v 5-6 Hinttenttu ubbay itti wozana gidiide, itti qaalaan Xoossaa, nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa Aawuwaa, bonchchana mala, genccuwanne minotethaa immiyaa Xoossay, hinttenttoo Kiristtoosi Yesuusi ootheeddawaadan, ittu ittuwaanna ittippe de7iyaa itti qofaa immo. 
\s1 Phawuloosa Oosuwaanne Ammanenna Asaw Gakkeedda Mishiraachchuwaa Qaalaa 
\p  
\v 7 Hewaa diraw, Kiristtoosi hinttentta mokkeeddawaadan, Xoossaa bonchchoo ittu ittuwaa mokkite.  
\v 8-9 Ayissi gooppe, Xoossay ammanetteeddawaa gidiyaawaa erissanaw, Xoossay aawatoo immana geeddawaa tumayanawunne Ayihuda gidenna asay Xoossaa A maarotethaa diraw bonchchanaw Kiristtoosi Ayihudatoo qooma gideeddawaa hinttenttoo oday. Hewaa Xoossaa Maxaafay, 
\q1 “Hewaa diraw, taani neena 
\q2 Ayihuda gidenna asaa giddon galatana; 
\q1 ne sunthaakka sabbana” 
\m yaagee. \x - \xo 15:8-9 \xt 2Sa 22:50; Maz 18:49\x* 
\q1  
\v 10 Qassikka, 
\q1 “Ayihuda gidenna asatoo, 
\q2 Xoossaa asatuwaanna nashettite” 
\m yaagee. \x - \xo 15:10 \xt Zar 32:43\x* 
\q1  
\v 11 Qassikka gujjiide, 
\q1 “Hinttenttoo, Ayihuda gidenna asatoo ubbatoo, 
\q2 Godaa galatite; asaw ubbaw, A galatite” 
\m yaagee. \x - \xo 15:11 \xt Maz 117:1\x* 
\q1  
\v 12 Qassikka Isiyaasi, 
\q1 “Issey zerethay yiide 
\q2 Ayihuda gidenna asaa mooddanaw denddana. 
\q1 Qassi unttunttu A bagganna demmana 
\q2 giide nashechchaan naagana” 
\m yaagee. \x - \xo 15:12 \xt Isa 11:10\x* 
\p  
\v 13 Hinttenttu akkana giide nashechchaan naagiyaawe Geeshsha Ayyaanaa wolqqaan diccanaadan, hinttenttoo immana geedda Xoossay, hintte A ammaniyaa diraw, hinttenttoo nashechchaanne sarotethaa kunthiide immo. 
\s1 Phawuloosi Xaliide Xaafeedda Gaasuwaa 
\p  
\v 14 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, hinttenttun lo77otethaynne eratethay ubbay kumeeddawaanne qassi ittu ittuwaa zoranaw danddayiyaawaa taani ta huuphew eraaddi.  
\v 15-16 Shin taani hinttentta ittibaa ittibaa gujja qofissanaw, ha dabidaabbiyaa giddon aynne yayyennaan hinttenttoo xaafaaddi. Taani Kiristtoosa Yesuusa qooma gidaade, Ayihuda gidenna asaw oothanaadan, Xoossay taw aadho keekatethaa immeedda diraw, taani aynne yayyabeykke; Ayihuda gidenna asay Geeshsha Ayyaanaa bagganna Xoossaw geeshsha gidiide, A nashechchiyaa yarshshuwaa gidanaadan, Xoossaa wonggalaa mishiraachchuwaa odiyaawaan geeshshatethaan oothay. 
\p  
\v 17 Hewaa diraw, taani Kiristtoosa Yesuusan gidaade Xoossaw oothiyaabaan ceeqettanaw danddayay.  
\v 18-19 Ayihuda gidenna asay Xoossaw azazettanaadan, Kiristtoosi ta bagganna qaalaan, oosuwan, mallaan, malaataa wolqqaaninne Geeshsha Ayyaanaa wolqqaan ootheeddawaa xalalaa taani odanaappe attin, harabaa odanaw xalikke. Hewaa diraw, Yeerusalaameppe doommaade, Iliwaariqoona geetettiyaa gadiyaa gakkanaw yuuyyaade, Kiristtoosa wonggalaa mishiraachchuwaa wurssa odaaddi.  
\v 20 Hawaadankka, taani hara asay doommeeddawaa bollan doommennaadan, Kiristtoosa sunthay xeesettibeennasan wonggalaa mishiraachchuwaa odanaw amottaaddi.  
\v 21 Shin Xoossaa Maxaafay, 
\q1 “Aabay hawaa gakkanaw odettibeennawanttu A be7anawantta; 
\q2 qassi aabaa sisibeennawanttu akeekanawantta” 
\m yaagee. \x - \xo 15:21 \xt Isa 52:15\x* 
\s1 Phawuloosi Roome Baanaw Qoppeedda 
\p  
\v 22 Hewaa diraw, taani cora wode hinttenttukko yaanaw koyyay; shin yaanaw danddayabeykke.  
\v 23 Shin taani ha77i ha heeraan ta oosuwaa wursseedda dirawunne cora laythaappe doommaade hinttentta baade be7anaw laamoteedda diraw  
\v 24 ha77ikka hinttenttukko baana gaade qoppay; taani Isippeene geetettiyaa gadiyaa baadde hinttentta be7anaw koyyay; qassi amareedda wodiyaa hinttentta be7aade nashettowaappe guyyiyan, Isippeene biishshin, hintte taana maaddana mala koyyay. 
\p  
\v 25 Shin ha77i taani Xoossaa asatuwaa maaddanaw, Yeerusalaame bay.  
\v 26 Ayissi gooppe, Maqidooniyaanne Akaayiyaa geetettiyaa gadiyaan de7iyaa woosa golle asatuu Yeerusalaamen de7iyaa hiyyeesatuwaassi miishshaa immanaw koyyeeddino.  
\v 27 Unttunttu barenttu huuphew hawaa oothanaw qofaa qachcheeddino. Unttunttu he hiyyeesatuwaa maaddanawe unttunttoo acuu de7ee; ayissi gooppe, Ayihudatuu barenttu ayyaanaa anjjuwaa Ayihuda gidenna asatuwaanna shaakkeeddawaa gidooppe, Ayihuda gidenna asatuukka qassi barenttoo de7eeddabaan Ayihudatuwaa maaddanaw bessee.  
\v 28 Hewaa diraw, taani ha oosuwaa wursseeddawaappe guyyiyaaninne unttunttoo shiiqeedda miishshaa ubbaa immeeddawaappe guyyiyan, Isippeene baadde hintte mataanna aadhdhana.  
\v 29 Taani hinttenttukko biyaa wode, Kiristtoosa anjjuu taanan kumina baanawaa eray. 
\p  
\v 30 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, taw Xoossaa hintte woossiidde, woosan hintte taananna minnanaadan, Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa baggannanne Geeshsha Ayyaanay immiyaa siiqotethan taani hinttentta woossay.  
\v 31 Taani Yihudaan de7iyaa ammanennawanttuppe attanaadaaninne qassi taani Yeerusalaamen oothiyaa oosuu yaani de7iyaa Xoossaa asatuwaa nashechchiyaawaa gidanaadan, Xoossaa woossite.  
\v 32 Qassi Xoossay gooppe, taani hinttenttukko nashechchaan baade, hintte matan shemppana.  
\v 33 Sarotethaa Xoossay hinttenttunna ubbaanna gido. Amen77i. 
\c 16  
\s1 Sarotaa 
\p  
\v 1 Kinkkiriyaa geetettiyaa katamaan de7iyaa ammaniyaa asaanna oothiyaa nu michchatta Peeba lo77o macca asa gidiyaawaa taani hinttentta erissay.  
\v 2 Hinttenttu izo geeshshatuu Godaa sunthan mokkiyaawaadan mokkite; qassi iza hinttenttuppe koyyiyaawe ayaa gidooppekka, izo maaddite; ayissi gooppe, iza bare huuphew cora asaa maaddaw; qassi taana ta huuphewukka darissa maaddaw. 
\p  
\v 3 Kiristtoosa Yesuusa oosuwaa taananna ittippe oothiyaa Phirisqqillissinne izi asinaa Aqiilassi ta sarotowaa odite.  
\v 4 Unttunttu ta shemppuwaa diraw, barenttu shemppuwaa aathi immeeddino. Unttuntta ta xalalaa gidennaan, Ayihuda gidenna asaa ammaniyaa asay ubbaykka galatee.  
\v 5 Qassi unttunttu golliyaa ammaniyaa asay shiiqiyaasaa udiide gakettiyaa asaa ubbaa saro giite. Iisiya gadiyan Kiristtoosa koyro ammaneedda ta siiqiyaa Eppanetoosaw, ta sarotowaa odite.  
\v 6 Hinttenttoo loytha daabureedda Mayraamo sarotite.  
\v 7 Taananna qasho gollen de7eedda ta dabbo gideedda Ayihudatuwaa, Anddironiqoosanne Yuuniyaasa sarotite. Yesuusi kiitteeddawanttu giddon unttunttu loythi eretteeddawantta. Qassi unttunttu Kiristtoosa taappe kasenna ammaneeddino. 
\p  
\v 8 Godaanna ittippetethaan de7iyaa ta siiqo laggiyaa Amppiliyaatoosaw ta sarotowaa odite.  
\v 9 Kiristtoosa oosuwaa nuunanna ittippe oothiyaa Urbbaanoosanne taani siiqiyaa Isxxaakusa sarotite.  
\v 10 Kiristtoosanna I de7iyaawe erettina paaciyaa xooneedda Apheliisaw ta sarotowaa odite; Arisxxobiloosa soy asawukka ta sarotowaa odite.  
\v 11 Ta dabbo gideedda Ayihudawiyaa Heeroodiyoonanne Kiristtoosa ammaniyaa Narssiisesa soy asaa sarotite. 
\p  
\v 12 Godaa oosuwan daaburiyaa Tirufaynanne Tirufooso geetettiyaa maccawantta sarotite; qassi Godaw daro daaburaade oothiyaa siiqiyaa Perssiiso sarotite.  
\v 13 Godaa oosuwan loythi eretteedda Rufoosayewunne taana bare na7aadan maaddeedda A daayiw ta sarotowaa odite.  
\v 14 Ta sarotowaa Asinkkiriitoosaw, Pileegoonaw, Hermeesaw, Patirobaasawunne unttunttunna de7iyaa ammaniyaa ishatuwaa ubbaw odite.  
\v 15 Pileegoona, Yuulo, Neeriyaa, A michchatto, Olumppoosanne unttunttunna de7iyaa Xoossaa asatuwaa ubbaa sarotite. 
\p  
\v 16 Geeshsha asaw bessiyaa yeretaa yerettiidde, ittu ittuwaa sarotite; Kiristtoosan ammaniyaawanttu ubbatuu hinttentta saro yaageeddino. 
\s1 Wurssethaa Zoriyaa 
\p  
\v 17 Taanaadan ammaniyaawanttoo, asaa giddon shaakotethaa medhdhiyaawantta, asaa ammanoo dhubo gidiyaawanttanne hintte tamaareedda timirttiyaanna gakettennawaa tamaarissiyaawantta akeekanaadan, taani hinttentta woossay. Unttunttukko shiiqoppite.  
\v 18 Ayissi gooppe, hewaa malabaa oothiyaawanttu barenttu uluwassi oothiinoppe attin, nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosaw oothikkino; barenttu labiyaa haasayaaninne qidhiyan iitabaa qoppenna asaa wozanaa balethiino.  
\v 19 Wonggalaw hintte azazetteeddawaa asay ubbay siseedda. Hewaa diraw, taani hintebaan nashettay; shin lo77otethaw hintte aadhdheedda eranchcha gidanaadaaninne qassi iitabaw ashikke gidanaadan koyyay.  
\v 20 Sarotethaa Xoossay Seexaanaa hintte gediyaappe garssanna haakkenna mata wode gaaccana. 
\p Nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa aadho keekatethay hinttenttunna gido. 
\p  
\v 21 Taananna oothiyaa Ximootoose hinttentta saro yaagee; qassi hawaadankka, ta dabbatuu Luuqiyoosi, Yaasooninne Sosiiphaaxiroosi hinttentta saro yaagiino. 
\p  
\v 22 Taani, Xarxxiyoosi, ha dabidaabbiyaa xaafeeddawe, hinttenttoo Godaa sunthan sarotaa kiittay. 
\p  
\v 23 Ammaniyaa asay ubbay A soyin shiiqiyaa ta siiraa Gaayoosi hinttentta saro yaagee; katamaa miishshaa oyqqiyaa Erasxxoosinne nu ishay Quwarxxoosi hinttentta saro yaagiino.  
\v 24 Nu Godaa Yesuusi Kiristtoosa aadho keekatethay hinttenttunna ubbaanna gido. Amen77i. 
\p  
\v 25 Nuuni Xoossaa galateetto. Taani wonggalaa bagganna Yesuusi Kiristtoosabaa odeeddawaadaninne daro wodiyaappe geemmiide, ha77i qoncceedda tumatethaadan, hintte ammanuwan hinttentta Xoossay minissanaw danddayee.  
\v 26 Shin ha77i nabatuu xaafeeddawaa bagganna tumatethay qoncciyaan erettannaadan ootheedda; qassi asaa ubbay Xoossaa ammaniide azazettanaadan, medhinaa Xoossaa azazuwan, ha alamiyaan de7iyaa asaa zerethaa ubbaw qoncceedda. 
\p  
\v 27 Aadhdheedda eratethay A xalalaw de7iyaa itti Xoossaw Yesuusi Kiristtoosa bagganna medhinaw bonchchuu gido. Amen77i.